NK104(phe)001:3896: zhes lnga pa bar mtshams med pa dbyings kyi gnad la brten nas /
NK104(phe)001:3897: rig pa dbyings dang ngo sprod par bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:3898: da ni drug pa yid ches gzhug pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma'i gnad la brten nas /
NK104(phe)001:3899: rtsa ba'i gnad kyis chos nyid mngon sum du mthong bar bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:3900: 'das pa'i sgron ma zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:3901: 'das pa'i ni rdza'i bum pa'i phyi'i nam mkha' lta bu chos kyi dbyings /
NK104(phe)001:3902: nang gi nam mkha' lta bu rang sems la lhad med pa /
NK104(phe)001:3903: bar gyi 'brel gyi nam mkha' lta bu thig le stong pa'i sgron ma de /
NK104(phe)001:3904: bar gyi 'brel gyi nam mkhas kyang nam mkha' phyi nang gi 'brel mtshon la /
NK104(phe)001:3905: nam mkha' rang gi ngo bo yin par gtan la phebs pas yid ches par byed la /
NK104(phe)001:3906: sgron ma 'dis kyang chos nyid gnyis kyi mtshams sbyar nas chos nyid du gtan la phebs nas /
NK104(phe)001:3907: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid yin par yid ches par byed pas na /
NK104(phe)001:3908: dang po dbang po brten pa'i gnad kyis dmar po shas che ba las /
NK104(phe)001:3909: de nas kha dog lnga'i 'od lnga'i 'od kyi thig
NK104(phe)001:3910: le rnams la sna yid ches pas gtad pa ni
NK104(phe)001:3911: / sngar gyi grogs dam pa mthong ba tsam gyis yid ches skye ba lta bu'o //
NK104(phe)001:3912: ma 'ongs pa'i ni de ltar yid ches par byas la /
NK104(phe)001:3913: da rnal 'byor pas lus rab tu dal ba brten la /
NK104(phe)001:3914: lus la khrus dag par byas la nyi ma la skam /
NK104(phe)001:3915: de nas mar sna tshogs pa bku mnye byas la
NK104(phe)001:3916: nyi ma la ha cang yang mi drag tsam bsro
NK104(phe)001:3917: // de nas gos grang dro ran par gon la /
NK104(phe)001:3918: rang gi mtheb 'dzub kyis dbang po rnams mar dwangs byed kyi rtsa gtem mo //
NK104(phe)001:3919: de ltar rgya mtsho ar gtad kyi nang nas byung ba ltar lhan cig gtems pa tsam las kyang /
NK104(phe)001:3920: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma rang gi lag tu
NK104(phe)001:3921: rma bya'i mdongs bzung ba ltar nges par snang ngo
NK104(phe)001:3922: // de ltar phyi ni de ltar snang ba'i sgron
NK104(phe)001:3923: ma de yang dang yang du gtems shing nyams su
NK104(phe)001:3924: blangs pas ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang ba rnams
NK104(phe)001:3925: la rang gi lag gis rtsa gtems pa'i rtsol ba
NK104(phe)001:3926: bya mi dgos par dbang po'i spyod yul du gsal
NK104(phe)001:3927: // ba ni / ye shes lnga'i rang rkyen dag
NK104(phe)001:3928: pas phyi yul la lhug par shar ba yin te
NK104(phe)001:3929: // ba ni / / de ni rtsa yang nas
NK104(phe)001:3930: yang du gtem pa las 'od snang dag par 'byung
NK104(phe)001:3931: // ba ni / / ba ni / thog ma
NK104(phe)001:3932: stong pa nyid chos thams cad kyi 'byung ba'i gnas
NK104(phe)001:3933: sgron ma las nyon mongs pa'i dri ma rang dag
NK104(phe)001:3935: de ni rang gi mig gi lta ba las 'byung
NK104(phe)001:3937: ba ste / 'di ltar byas pas sgron ma nyid
NK104(phe)001:3940: rtsa gtem pa'i gnad dang bral ba'i dus sgron ma
NK104(phe)001:3941: nyid du mnyam pa nyid du ye nas snang ba
NK104(phe)001:3942: yid la / 'phral du byas pas byung ba lta bu ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:3943: zhes drug pa yid ches gzhug pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma'i gnad la brten nas /
NK104(phe)001:3944: rtsa'i gnad kyis chos nyid mngon sum du mthong bar bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:3945: da ni bdun pa lhun grub snang tshul 'od kyi
NK104(phe)001:3946: snang ba la brten nas chos nyid kyi bar ma
NK104(phe)001:3947: do la ye shes ma bu 'phrad par byed pa'i
NK104(phe)001:3949: 'das pa'i 'od rnams la zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:3950: 'das pa'i ni lhun grub rin po che sna tshogs
NK104(phe)001:3951: ma nges pa'i snang ba la 'od ltar 'char ba'i
NK104(phe)001:3952: sgo las / rang snang khyab par ston pa'i 'od ces bya ba ngo ma shes pa las /
NK104(phe)001:3954: de yang gang dang gnyis 'khrul na /
NK104(phe)001:3955: rigs drug so so'i rtags mtshon pa rang bzhin kun khyab kyi 'od dang /
NK104(phe)001:3957: srid pa'i bar do la dbang po kun tshang thogs med rgyu'i lus bzung nas /
NK104(phe)001:3958: de nas sdug bsngal skye zhing 'khor mar spyad nas /
NK104(phe)001:3959: las kyi mtha' so so'i las kyi dbang gis rigs drug so so'i lus su 'khor zhing len pas /
NK104(phe)001:3960: rang bzhin gyi bar dor 'khor bas na 'khor ba zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:3961: de ltar dus thams cad 'khor ba rnams la lam
NK104(phe)001:3962: thog mar yang lhun grub nas 'od ma shes pa
NK104(phe)001:3963: las 'khrul la / srid pa'i bar do la yang
NK104(phe)001:3964: so so'i lus gang len pa'i 'od la gnas la
NK104(phe)001:3965: las 'khrul la / / da lta yang gzhi mtshon pa'i 'od gnas pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:3966: phyis kyang chos nyid bar do'i 'od la lam btod nas 'gro bas na /
NK104(phe)001:3967: 'di nyid du chos nyid kyi bar do nges 'dzin
NK104(phe)001:3968: par byed pa'i 'od gtan la phebs par byed pa
NK104(phe)001:3970: ma 'ongs pa'i 'od snang ba rgya che ba'i 'od ston par byed pa'i 'od ni /
NK104(phe)001:3975: gnan na nems bzhin pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:3977: de yang ye shes kyi rlan gyis khyab pas ltem pa /
NK104(phe)001:3978: ye shes kyi mdangs ston pas mer ba /
NK104(phe)001:3979: ye shes kyi rlung gis 'gul ba /
NK104(phe)001:3981: lus kyi rdos pa zad pas nem pa /
NK104(phe)001:3984: rigs kyi tshom bu'i 'od ye shes kyi rtsal rdzogs pas rigs lnga'i 'od dang /
NK104(phe)001:3985: ye shes kyi mkhyen pa'i rang snang bas tshom bu dang /
NK104(phe)001:3986: ye shes kyi zung 'jug lam du rdzogs pas yab yum du snang ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:3987: ye shes kyi lam mngon du gyur pas ye shes
NK104(phe)001:3988: bzhi sbyor gyi 'od rnams la da lta'i dus na
NK104(phe)001:3990: chos nyid kyi bar do la snang ba rnam par
NK104(phe)001:3991: dag pa de la sems rang bzhin gyis mnyam pa
NK104(phe)001:3992: nyid bzhag par 'byung bar nges so //
NK104(phe)001:3993: de ltar sems can 'khor bar 'khyams kyang zhag lnga bde dang ldan zhes pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:3994: 'di'i dus na bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:3996: rjes su dran pa la sogs pa 'char par 'og nas ston no //
NK104(phe)001:3997: da ltar gyi 'od ni thig le stong pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:3998: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron me'i 'od dang /
NK104(phe)001:3999: nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i 'od rnams la
NK104(phe)001:4000: blo rtse gcig phab pa'i ni dus thams cad ma
NK104(phe)001:4002: bar ma do mi dgos par 'di nyid la zag bcas mi snang bar sangs rgya bar nges so //
NK104(phe)001:4003: de ltar brtan pa thob nas 'khrul pa'i snang ba
NK104(phe)001:4004: thams cad la rang gi 'od lnga'i rgyas thebs pa
NK104(phe)001:4005: zhes bya'o // 'di ni da ltar 'od rang snang du shes pa'i dus dang /
NK104(phe)001:4006: bar ma dor longs spyod pa'i dus dang /
NK104(phe)001:4007: lhun grub la rang rdzogs pa'i dus dang gsum ngo
NK104(phe)001:4008: sprad pa'i dus na mnyam pa nyid du ye nas
NK104(phe)001:4011: zhes bdun pa de dag gis ni spyi don bzhi
NK104(phe)001:4012: pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad dus
NK104(phe)001:4013: gsum mnyam pa nyid mu mtha' dang bral bar bstan
NK104(phe)001:4014: pa'o // da ni spyi don lnga la dus gsum
NK104(phe)001:4015: gnyam pa nyid kyi 'bru bshad pa dris lan bcas
NK104(phe)001:4016: par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK104(phe)001:4017: dri ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4019: dri ba mdor bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4020: de nas yang 'od zer kun 'dul byang chub sems la sogs pa bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:4022: lan rgyas par bshad pa la nang don gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po //
NK104(phe)001:4023: chos nyid rnam par dag pa dus kyi gnad la rten nas rtogs par bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4024: ston pa kun tu bzang pos zhal gyi la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:4025: ston pa ni yon tan khyad par dang ldan pa'i sgo nas smos te /
NK104(phe)001:4026: kun tu mang po'am rgya che ba la bya la /
NK104(phe)001:4027: bzang po'i 'khor ba'i mtha' mya ngan las log pa /
NK104(phe)001:4028: zhal 'dzum pa ni sems can gyi rgyud tshim par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4029: de yang gong gi mdzad pa'i stobs las byung ba ste /
NK104(phe)001:4030: 'di dag ni dri ba gsum pa'i don bka' stsal to //
NK104(phe)001:4031: bdag don du kye ma zhes chos nyid mngon sum du rtogs par gyis shig /
NK104(phe)001:4032: kye ma zhes gzhan don du 'pho ba chen mo'i lus thob par gyis shig /
NK104(phe)001:4033: ces ston pas nyan pa po'i rgyud sbyangs nas /
NK104(phe)001:4034: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'od zer kun 'dul zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:4036: sngon ni skal pa bdun stong gi sngon rol nas
NK104(phe)001:4037: yul dbyangs kyi nyan thos la sogs shin tu gsang
NK104(phe)001:4039: de las kyang dbus na sangs rgyas rnams kyis rnam
NK104(phe)001:4040: par brgyan pa'i shing sa la rnam par bkod par
NK104(phe)001:4041: bya bar / ston pa kun tu bzang po ngas /
NK104(phe)001:4042: 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje sems dpa'
NK104(phe)001:4043: la sogs pa rnams la 'di skad du chos nyid
NK104(phe)001:4044: rnam par dag pa'i lung bstan pa yin no //
NK104(phe)001:4045: zhes 'od zer kun 'dul la bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:4046: kye zhes 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:4047: dad pa la sogs pa dbang po phyin ci ma log par nyon cig /
NK104(phe)001:4048: rtogs pa nyid rang lugs su skye ba'i dus bstan par bya'o bar bskul nas /
NK104(phe)001:4049: snang ba dang dngos po dang stong pas khyab pas thams cad rang la spros bcas dang /
NK104(phe)001:4051: shin tu spros pa med pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4052: rab tu spros pa med pa'i dbang du gyur nas /
NK104(phe)001:4053: bla ma mchog tu dag pa la man ngag dag
NK104(phe)001:4054: pa rang gi rig pa mngon sum du ston pa'i
NK104(phe)001:4055: gnad dang / sngon byung du ston pas ston pa'i dus kyi tshe /
NK104(phe)001:4056: chos nyid de bsgom pa ma byas kyang /
NK104(phe)001:4057: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i dgongs pa'i bden pa mthong nas /
NK104(phe)001:4058: rang gi chos nyid longs pa'i dus zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4059: de nas phyi rol gyi rags pa'i snang ba goms pa'i stobs la brten nas /
NK104(phe)001:4060: ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang ba thams cad du rang thad du shar te /
NK104(phe)001:4061: nyams gong nas gong du shar ba rnams kyi rig pa dang dbyings kyi sa bon 'phel ba'i tshe /
NK104(phe)001:4062: rig pa nyid tshad la phebs pas dper na bre tshad srang tshad lta bu'i dus zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4063: yang skyes bu lus kyi 'byung ba bzhi'i stobs rgas pas zas nas /
NK104(phe)001:4064: snang ba rags pa'i stobs nang gi 'byung ba nub nas /
NK104(phe)001:4065: 'du shes rnams kha nang du bltas pa'i tshe //
NK104(phe)001:4066: rang gi rig pa'i byung rang ngo la 'debs pa'i dus zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4067: yang chos nyid bar ma do la rang gi chos
NK104(phe)001:4068: nyid 'byung rkyen dang bral nas 'od kyi snang ba
NK104(phe)001:4069: thams cad bde bar brdal ba'i tshe /
NK104(phe)001:4070: phyi'i 'byung bar rags pa rnams chos nyid ma'i snang ba la thim pas /
NK104(phe)001:4071: rig pa bu dang gnyis ngo shes pas mnyam pa'i dus zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4072: 'di'i dus na sangs rgyas rnams kyi bden pa'i 'od
NK104(phe)001:4073: zer gyis rnal 'byor rang ngo'i las gang zhing rgyas
NK104(phe)001:4074: nas chos sku longs sku sprul sku rnams mngon par
NK104(phe)001:4076: dgongs pa nyid brten pa rang gis rang la thob pa'i dus zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4077: zhes dang po chos nyid rnam par dag pa dus kyi gnad la brten nas /
NK104(phe)001:4079: da ni gnyis pa mngon sum ma bcos pa grangs
NK104(phe)001:4080: kyi gnad la brten nas rtogs par bstan pa ni
NK104(phe)001:4081: / kye ma kye ma 'khor gyi byang chub sems
NK104(phe)001:4082: dpa' rnams nyon cig ces pa la sogs pas bstan
NK104(phe)001:4083: / te / de ltar sdud pa po la gdams pa dang bcas pas lung bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:4084: lta ba stong pas ni chos thams cad bdag med du rtogs pas /
NK104(phe)001:4085: rang gi sems la gnas lugs kyis rgyas thebs so //
NK104(phe)001:4086: sgom pa gnyis med 'od rang la gsal bas brjod du med pa'i don rgyud la skyes te /
NK104(phe)001:4087: mtha' dang bral ba'i gnad kyi ngag la smra snying mi 'dod pa'i rgyas thebs so //
NK104(phe)001:4088: spyod pa snang ba rgyas 'debs kyis ci byas thams
NK104(phe)001:4089: cad 'gro ba la phan pas lus kyi byed spyod
NK104(phe)001:4090: thams cad tshogs su gyur pa'i byas thebs pa ni
NK104(phe)001:4091: / skye med stong pa'i 'bras bu rang gi lus kyi thob pa'i dus gsum zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4092: de ltar gsum 'du 'bral med par zang thal gnyis
NK104(phe)001:4093: med kyi 'bras bu ni chos kyi sku tshig gis
NK104(phe)001:4094: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i rtsal 'khor 'das
NK104(phe)001:4095: gang du yang ma grub pa thob bo //
NK104(phe)001:4096: chos nyid kyi rang bzhin la 'gag pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:4097: longs sku tshig dang bral ba'i bar lhun grub bcos pa med par gzung ste /
NK104(phe)001:4098: de nyid las thugs rje rang shugs su ma 'gags
NK104(phe)001:4099: pa la sprul sku mtshan dang bral ba'i rtsa ba
NK104(phe)001:4100: rang khyab kun la snang bar bcad pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4101: rnal 'byor pa'i lus ngag la drod rtags mthar phyin gyi lus sprul skur grol ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:4103: sems chos skur grol ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:4104: gsum ye nas rang gi lus ngag sems la rdzogs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4105: bdag nyid kyis bdag nyid kyi snang ba mthong ba'i dus gsum zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4106: rig pa'i ngo bo yul la sprad pa ni sprin
NK104(phe)001:4107: la sogs pa'i sgrib phyogs dang 'byung ba gzhan gyi
NK104(phe)001:4108: rkyen rdul dang kha char la sogs pa dang bral
NK104(phe)001:4109: ba'i nam mkhar rig pa gang la yang ma brten
NK104(phe)001:4110: na / dper na thog lta bu ye shes dag pa'i rlung gis bul ba 'phangs te /
NK104(phe)001:4111: mi mgul ba gsum la gzhi bcas pa'i rig pa
NK104(phe)001:4112: mi 'gyur ba rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi gzer
NK104(phe)001:4113: dbyings rig 'bral ba med par btab nas /
NK104(phe)001:4114: ye shes 'byung ba gzigs stangs ma 'das pa'i rgya mtsho'i mig chu'i rang bzhin /
NK104(phe)001:4115: snang byed kyi ni phyi yul /
NK104(phe)001:4116: lcags kyus 'khor ba dang ye shes kyi gzugs 'dzin pa /
NK104(phe)001:4117: de nyid dbyings rig 'bral ba med pa /
NK104(phe)001:4118: rang bzung ba ni gzhan ma yin pa'i chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4119: de ni yang nas yang du goms par byas pas rang shugs kyi dus gsum zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4120: zhes gnyis pa mngon sum ma bcos pa grangs kyi gnad la brten nas rtogs par bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:4121: da ni gsum pa mnyam pa nyid mu mtha' dang
NK104(phe)001:4122: bral ba'i gnad la brten nas chos nyid phyogs cha
NK104(phe)001:4123: dang bral bar bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4124: e ma ho 'khor gyi zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:4125: e ma zhes ngo mtshar dang bcas pa'i sgo nas
NK104(phe)001:4126: ston pa nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor gyi byang
NK104(phe)001:4127: chub sems dpa' 'od zer kun 'dus la sogs pa
NK104(phe)001:4128: rnams nyon cig ces bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:4129: chos nyid ni spros pa thams cad dang bral ba /
NK104(phe)001:4130: ma bcos pas ni lus ngag sems kyi bya byed
NK104(phe)001:4131: rang sor gzhag pas mnyam pa nyid mtha' gang la
NK104(phe)001:4133: de lta bu'i chos nyid bcos ma las grol ba'i klong gang dang yang ma 'dres pa nyid du /
NK104(phe)001:4134: sangs rgyas 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar bzhugs pa kun gyi mdzad spyod ni /
NK104(phe)001:4135: chos kyi sku'i mdzad spyod mi mdzad mnyam nyid du mdzad /
NK104(phe)001:4136: longs sku yis snang ngo rang dag tu spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4137: sprul pa'i skus sna tshogs dbyer med kyi ngang du rang snang ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4138: 'khor 'das gnyis su ye nas grub pa med par
NK104(phe)001:4139: rang ngo la gnas pas na mnyam pa zhes chen
NK104(phe)001:4140: po bya'o // yang rjes 'jug gi dus na rten
NK104(phe)001:4141: gyi gang zag dad pa dang ldan pa zhig gis
NK104(phe)001:4142: po bya'o // / bla ma'i man ngag gnad du 'gro ba zhig la /
NK104(phe)001:4143: brtson 'grus bstan nas nyams su blangs pas /
NK104(phe)001:4144: dbyings dang rig pa la goms pa'i gnad kyis nyams kyi snang ba mthong ba'i tshe /
NK104(phe)001:4145: 'khrul pa bdag 'dzin gyi yul yod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4148: mi snang ba la sogs pa du ma zhen pa rang rgyud pa 'gags nas /
NK104(phe)001:4149: nyams kyi snang ba tsam du yang 'dzin pa med pa'i tshe /
NK104(phe)001:4150: chos nyid zad pa 'bras bu ye dag chen po'i chos nyid ces bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4151: rang byung gi ye shes la rang shar ba'i tshe /
NK104(phe)001:4152: chos thams cad tshad du phyin pas nyams su blang ba gdeng du tshud pa zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4153: 'di'i dus chos cer mthong du mthong bas lta ba zhes bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4154: de las 'bral ba med pas bsgom pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:4155: de nyid las gzhan du 'gro sa med pas spyod pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4156: de ltar de dag rnams tha dad pa ma yin
NK104(phe)001:4157: par gnyis su med par 'dus pas na srog med
NK104(phe)001:4159: de la ming du btags na rang gnas yongs 'dres kyi mnyam pa zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4160: zhes gsum pa la mnyam pa nyid mu mtha' med pa'i gnad la brten nas /
NK104(phe)001:4161: chos nyid phyogs cha dang bral bar bstan nas //
NK104(phe)001:4162: da ni bzhi pa chos nyid bcos ma las grol
NK104(phe)001:4163: ba'i gnad la brten nas nyi bdun cig tu bsre
NK104(phe)001:4165: kye 'khor gyi zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:4166: sdud pa po byang chub sems dpa' bskul lo kye
NK104(phe)001:4167: zhes 'khor rnams kyi nang byang chub sems dpa' 'od
NK104(phe)001:4168: zer kun 'dul la sogs pa rnams nyon cig ces
NK104(phe)001:4169: bos nas / dri ma ni gnyis te /
NK104(phe)001:4170: rang bzhin gyi dri ma dang /
NK104(phe)001:4172: rang bzhin ni kun tu bzang po la sogs pa'i ye ji bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la /
NK104(phe)001:4173: dge ba la rdul tsam cig ma byas kyang gzhi
NK104(phe)001:4174: mngon du gyur nas sangs rgyas pas dri ma ye
NK104(phe)001:4176: khams gsum gyis sems can gyi sdig pa skad cig
NK104(phe)001:4177: tsam yang ma byas kyang khams gsum du ltung ba
NK104(phe)001:4178: ni / rang bzhin gyi dri ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:4179: bsags pa so so'i lus ngag la bskal pa thog
NK104(phe)001:4180: ma nas las kyi 'phel shugs kyis bsags pa'i rnam
NK104(phe)001:4181: par smin pa las byung ba'i las kyi dri ma
NK104(phe)001:4182: dang / nyon mongs pa bag la nyal ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:4183: mngon du rgyu sna tshogs las byung zhing bsags pa'i nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dang /
NK104(phe)001:4184: skal pa dpag tu med pa nas bsags pa'i grub
NK104(phe)001:4185: pa'i mtha' rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i shes bya'i dri
NK104(phe)001:4186: ma'o // de yang dri ma rnams rang sar dag
NK104(phe)001:4187: pa'i rnal 'byor pa la chos kyi sku zhes las
NK104(phe)001:4188: dag pas chos nyid la sbyor ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4189: 'di ni dngos gzhi las khyad par du sngon 'gro'i bye brag yin te /
NK104(phe)001:4191: rig pa ni gsal byed gzhan la rag ma lus pa /
NK104(phe)001:4192: rnal du lus ngag yid dal brten pas phebs de la chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4193: de la ming du btags na /
NK104(phe)001:4194: dran pa rang gis dag pa'i dgongs pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:4195: de nyid sems dang sems kyi 'du byed kyis 'dzin pa ngang gis nus pas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4196: de yang nyams gong 'phel gyi dus sam /
NK104(phe)001:4197: chos nyid bar do'i dus na /
NK104(phe)001:4198: phra ba rdul rags pa'i ri rab la sogs pa'i
NK104(phe)001:4199: 'byung ba lnga rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i dngos po
NK104(phe)001:4205: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i yul dang bral bas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4206: de yang dngos po mthar 'dzin pa ma yin pas /
NK104(phe)001:4207: stong pa ye nas sangs rgyas sems can thams cad la khyab pa'i chos nyid la /
NK104(phe)001:4208: sems med pa'i phyir dbyings dang rig pa la lta
NK104(phe)001:4209: byed kyi gzhi zad pas rig pa tshad phebs kyi
NK104(phe)001:4210: sar phyin pas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4211: phyi'i 'byung ba sa chu me rlung /
NK104(phe)001:4212: nang gi 'byung ba sha khrag drod dbugs zad pa'i rang gi lus 'od gsal du 'gro ba la /
NK104(phe)001:4213: 'od lnga ye shes lnga zung du 'jug pas chod nyid ces pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4214: de ltar chos nyid zad pa la ma rig pa
NK104(phe)001:4215: ye nas dag pas rang gi gnas lugs ka nas
NK104(phe)001:4217: phyi nang so sor zhen pa'i snang ba rang sar grol bas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4218: de ltar rnal 'byor pa'i blo la skyes pas rang gi rgyud kyang dag ste /
NK104(phe)001:4219: da chos nyiid las grol sa gang yang med do //
NK104(phe)001:4220: de lta bu'i chos nyid de yang thog ma yul
NK104(phe)001:4221: ma dag pa la 'dzin pa rang rgyud pas gzungs
NK104(phe)001:4222: pas nyon mongs phra ba'i phra ba las /
NK104(phe)001:4223: 'khor ba'i las tha dad par song ba yang bla
NK104(phe)001:4224: ma'i man ngag gsang ba dang phrad pas chos nyid
NK104(phe)001:4225: do // zhes mnyam pa nyid mu mtha' dang bral
NK104(phe)001:4226: ba'i gnad la brten nas chos nyid phyogs cha dang
NK104(phe)001:4228: de dag gis ni spyi don lnga pa la gsum du byas nas bstan no //
NK104(phe)001:4229: de dag hril gyis log pas le'u gzhung la bsdus pa'i don ltar bsdus nas bstan no //
NK104(phe)001:4231: zhes kun tu la sogs pa mtshan gyi skabs su bstan no //
NK104(phe)001:4232: rang bzhin ni ma bcos pa /
NK104(phe)001:4233: rdzogs pa chen po ni ma rdzogs gang yang med pa phyogs gang du yang ma lhung pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4235: chos de shes pa tsam gyis rigs drug tu mi 'khor bar bstan pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4236: chos thams cad ni spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid do //
NK104(phe)001:4237: dus ni 'das pa ma 'ongs pa da ltar gsum mo //
NK104(phe)001:4239: de ltar rnal 'byor pa'i rgyud la /
NK104(phe)001:4240: chos nyid du mnyam par rdzogs so ni dum bu'i lhag ma med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4241: lha'i ni 'di la khams gsum tshang ste /
NK104(phe)001:4244: gzugs med pa'i khams dang gsum lha la tshang bas /
NK104(phe)001:4245: de yang 'dod chags bzhi las gzhag pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4246: 'khyud pa dang lag bcang gnyis la dngos su spyod pas 'dod khams so //
NK104(phe)001:4247: bltas pas tshim pa gzugs kyi khams la yod pas
NK104(phe)001:4248: gzugs mdzes pa la bltas nas bgad pas tshim pa
NK104(phe)001:4249: gzugs kyi khams zhes bya la /
NK104(phe)001:4250: nyon mongs bag nyal las mngon gyur gyi rten med pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4251: gzugs med pa'i khams zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4252: yang na 'dod pa spyod pas na 'dod khams so //
NK104(phe)001:4253: gzugs dang lang tsho la spyod pas gzugs khams so //
NK104(phe)001:4254: rdul cha dang bcas pa'i gzugs med pas gzugs med pa'i khams so //
NK104(phe)001:4255: yang na rgyu dug gsum gyis byas pas khams gsum du byung ste /
NK104(phe)001:4258: gti mug gsum gyi rgyu las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4259: 'o na de dag lha la tshang pa de ci las byung zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:4260: nga rgyal khengs pa dang bcas bcas pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4261: skye gnas ni 'dod pa'i khams kyi lha la gnas rigs drug yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4262: 'di'i rgyu rkyen gang las byung na /
NK104(phe)001:4263: las rgya bsten pas 'dod chags rang rgyud du song ba las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4264: de yang de dag gi ming dang /
NK104(phe)001:4268: gzhal yas khang gi tshad dang /
NK104(phe)001:4273: snang ba'i tshad dang dgus bstan to //
NK104(phe)001:4280: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed dang drug go /
NK104(phe)001:4281: de dag gi lus bong gi tshad dang /
NK104(phe)001:4283: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i lus kyi tshad khru brgyad dang /
NK104(phe)001:4285: tshe lo stong phrag lnga thub /
NK104(phe)001:4286: gnas ni ri rab kyi bang rim dang po'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4287: gser gyi 'khor lo can zhes bya ba'i sa gzhi rab tu mnyam pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4288: gser gyi bye ma bdal bas rab tu khod snyoms pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4289: re re la dpag tshad lnga stong pa'i gzhal med
NK104(phe)001:4290: khang rin po che gser zhun ma las grub pa
NK104(phe)001:4291: / lha'i sil snyan dang rol mo sna tshogs pa 'char bar byed pa gnyis yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4292: ri rab kyi cog gzhi la 'khor lo gser gyi sgra 'byin pa /
NK104(phe)001:4293: zhes bya ba'i gnas su mi gdags su btub pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4294: longs spyod ni dga' ba dang bde ba 'ba' zhig la spyod do //
NK104(phe)001:4295: de yang sdug bsngal du lha min dang 'tha' ba che ste /
NK104(phe)001:4297: thog ma sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas nas lha rgod po cig gis /
NK104(phe)001:4298: dpag bsam gyi shing ro brgya dang ldan pa cig gi mur pa'i 'phro la ltung bas /
NK104(phe)001:4299: lha min gyi bu mo chu lde ma gcig gi chu snod du byung nas /
NK104(phe)001:4300: de'i byin brlabs sam yon tan las /
NK104(phe)001:4301: chu de yang ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa gcig tu gyur pa las /
NK104(phe)001:4302: de'i ro la lha min rnams 'dus pas /
NK104(phe)001:4303: rab tu dga' nas 'di dag gang las byung byas pas /
NK104(phe)001:4304: 'di shing gi 'brum bu 'di nam mkha' las byung bas lags so byas pas /
NK104(phe)001:4305: lha min rgad po cig na re /
NK104(phe)001:4307: ldan pa 'di lha rnams la yod pa yin pa las /
NK104(phe)001:4308: lha min thams cad 'dus la dmag drangs la phog go zer nas /
NK104(phe)001:4309: dee nas sna tshogs yid 'khrug par byed pa zhes
NK104(phe)001:4310: bya ba'i tshal du 'tshogs shing gros byas nas lha
NK104(phe)001:4312: thog mar gnod sbyin rnams dang 'thab /
NK104(phe)001:4313: des ma thub pas bar snang gi lha bran rnams dang 'thab /
NK104(phe)001:4314: des kyang ma thub pas rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i lha rnams dang 'thab pas /
NK104(phe)001:4315: de ltar 'thab rtsod kyi duhkha yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4316: lha 'di dag kun rgyu gang las byung na /
NK104(phe)001:4317: snga ma sbyin pa las byung zhing /
NK104(phe)001:4318: 'di nas tshe 'phos nas lha min nam /
NK104(phe)001:4319: la la rgya rigs su skye ba yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4320: de nas tshe 'phos ma thag tu thar pa la le los g.yeng ba'i dbang gis /
NK104(phe)001:4321: yi dwags phyi'i sgrib pa can du skye'o //
NK104(phe)001:4322: de nas sems can dmyal bar skye ba ra 'gyur ro //
NK104(phe)001:4323: zas ni shing thog ngo mtshar can za zhing /
NK104(phe)001:4324: gos ras dang dar sna tshogs pa gon pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4325: snang ba tsam skyed mos tshal dang kun dga' ra bar mthong ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4326: rgyal chen ni mi'i rigs kyi rgyal chen rnams las 'phags pas na rgyal chen la /
NK104(phe)001:4327: rigs ni dga' ba'i rigs dang /
NK104(phe)001:4329: 'grogs dag'i dang bde skyong gi rigs dang bzhi yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4330: de dag kyang gser dang dngul dang zangs dang /
NK104(phe)001:4332: stong stong re res sprul pa 'gyed nus pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4334: shar lho na glang po che la zhon cing zangs kyi tsakra thogs pa sha stag /
NK104(phe)001:4335: byang shar na khyung la zhon cing lcags kyi tsakra thogs pa sha stag go /
NK104(phe)001:4336: lha min de g.yul 'gyed pa'i dus na /
NK104(phe)001:4337: lha'i bsod nams kyi stobs kyis /
NK104(phe)001:4338: 'khor lo de dag las mtshon rigs mi 'dra ba stong stong du sprul par nus pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4339: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lus bong gi tshad ni /
NK104(phe)001:4342: tshe lo khri phrag lnga thub pa /
NK104(phe)001:4343: gnas ni ri rab kyi steng na rdo ar mo leb na /
NK104(phe)001:4344: glang po che rab tu bstan pa'i dpung zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4345: dpag bsam shing gi rtsa ba la yang dag par bkod pa'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4346: ri rab kyi steng dang mnyam pa'i tshad /
NK104(phe)001:4347: rin po che brgya rtsa cig las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4348: de'i phyogs bzhir tshal po dga' ba'i tshal dang /
NK104(phe)001:4352: mdun na chos bzang zhes bya ba'i lha'i mdun sa /
NK104(phe)001:4353: sman 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i mdun sa yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4354: de nas longs spyod kyi tshad gzhon pa sna tshogs dang /
NK104(phe)001:4356: sil snyan sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4357: sdug bsngal ni lha min dang 'thab ste /
NK104(phe)001:4358: de yang rgyal chen bzhis ma thub pas 'dir dmag 'ong ste /
NK104(phe)001:4359: lho'i phyogs su 'dres pas 'dres pa'i tshal zhes bya /
NK104(phe)001:4360: nub kyi phyogs su bsad pa dang rgyal ba la sogs pa grangs med pa byung bas /
NK104(phe)001:4362: lha'i bsod nams kyi stobs kyi shi ba shi la /
NK104(phe)001:4363: ma shi ba smas pa tsam 'dun sa sman 'tsho
NK104(phe)001:4364: byed gzhon nu'i ldum rar khrid pa tsam gyis sos
NK104(phe)001:4366: lha rnams rgyal na shar du 'tshogs nas dga' bas na dga' ba'i tshal zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4367: rgyal ba'i tshe na byang phyogs su song nas /
NK104(phe)001:4368: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la mos shing 'dun pa'i sgo nas gsol ba 'debs pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4370: pham na brgyal zhing sdug bsngal bas mya ngan gyi khang par 'dug go /
NK104(phe)001:4371: ltung ba ni snga la tshogs rdzogs par byas pas mir ltung /
NK104(phe)001:4373: de las ngan song du rims kyis song snang ba
NK104(phe)001:4374: me tog dang rol mor btang snyoms su gnas pa'i
NK104(phe)001:4377: 'dir skyes pa'i lha rnams kyang bu sum cu rtsa
NK104(phe)001:4378: gnyis brgya byin lha'i gtso bo dang rtsa gsum du
NK104(phe)001:4380: de yang bsod nams kyi glang po che la mche ba drug pa yod pa la /
NK104(phe)001:4381: de re re'i nang du chu yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i rdzing bu re re /
NK104(phe)001:4382: de re re'i nang nas khrus byed pa'i lha mo lnga brgya lnga brgya yod pas /
NK104(phe)001:4383: lha mo de dag re re la rma bya lnga
NK104(phe)001:4384: lnga dang ne tso mi skad shes pa lnga lnga
NK104(phe)001:4385: dang / sgra mi 'dra ba lnga stong lnga stong la sogs te /
NK104(phe)001:4386: dri dang 'dod pa'i yon tan de yod pa rab tu 'phro ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4387: glang po che mgo bo sum cu rtsa gnyis gser las byung ba /
NK104(phe)001:4388: g.yu mgo gcig dang rtsa gsum gyi steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4389: gser mgo la sras rnams zhon la /
NK104(phe)001:4390: g.yu mgo'i steng brgya byin lha'i dbang po 'khor lnga stong lnga brgya dang bcas pa gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:4391: sras de dag re re la yang 'khor lnga brgya lnga brgyas bskor nas yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4392: glang po de 'dra ba re re'i 'khor na nye ba'i 'khor ma gtogs pa'i /
NK104(phe)001:4393: lha'i bu bye ba phrag khrig drug cu drug cu gnas pa'o /
NK104(phe)001:4394: nye dbang sum cu rtsa gnyis la btsun mo lnga brgya lnga brgya yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:4395: btsun mo re re la g.yog mo lnga brgya lnga brgya yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4396: brgya byin nyid la btsun mo lnga stong yod la /
NK104(phe)001:4397: de dag re re la g.yog mi lnga stong lnga stong /
NK104(phe)001:4398: de dag re re la lha'i bu sum cu rtsa gnyis yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4399: de'i phyir na sum cu rtsa gsum pa zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4400: 'di yan chad na 'dod chags lag bcangs pas tshim pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4401: 'thab bral gyi lus kyi tshad khru sum cu rtsa bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4404: gnas ni dpag bsam shing gi rtse mo la /
NK104(phe)001:4405: rin po che sna tshogs kyi lo 'dab rgyas pa zhes bya ba na /
NK104(phe)001:4406: gzhal med khang rin po che dgu stong brgya las
NK104(phe)001:4407: grub pa ri rab kyi steng gnyis dang ldan pa
NK104(phe)001:4408: / longs spyod dga' ba dang bde ba spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4409: duhkha ltung ba las med do //
NK104(phe)001:4411: zas gos dga' ba za zhing bde ba gyon pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4412: snang ba sna tshogs par snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4414: 'di yan chad lha min gyi 'thab pa dang bral bas 'thab bral zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4415: 'khor rnams longs spyod brjod kyis mi long ngo //
NK104(phe)001:4416: dga' ldan gyi lus khru brgya nyer brgyad /
NK104(phe)001:4419: gnas rin po che 'thon 'thing zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4420: sa gzhi thams cad rin po che sil mar bdal ba'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4421: ri rab kyi steng bzhi dang mnyam pa yod la /
NK104(phe)001:4422: longs spyod rtag tu dga' ba dang ldan zhing bde ba la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4423: du kha dran pa'i tshe na ltung ba che'o //
NK104(phe)001:4424: zas dga' ba dang yengs pa la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4425: snang ba sgra brnyan sna tshogs dang /
NK104(phe)001:4426: dri zhim po'i tshogs dpag tu med par snang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:4427: yon tan ni 'og ma las tshe tshad la sogs pa'i 'gyur yod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4428: dga' ldan zhes bya ba ni rtag tu dga' ba 'ba' zhig la spyod pa la /
NK104(phe)001:4430: sngon gyi gnas la sogs pa dran pa 'byung bas /
NK104(phe)001:4431: ltung ba'i duhkha skad cig tsam re 'byang ba las /
NK104(phe)001:4432: lhag ma dga' ba dang ldan pas na dga' ldan zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4433: de ni sems longs spyod pa la yengs pas bde ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4434: 'phrul dag'i lus khru nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa drug /'od khru gang pa /
NK104(phe)001:4436: gnas rab tu sprul pa can zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4437: nyin zhag re re la rin po che'i rigs mi
NK104(phe)001:4438: 'dra ba brgya phrag du mar 'gyur bar nus pa'o
NK104(phe)001:4439: // de yang kha dog dkar ba la dkar ba'i mdangs yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:4441: de lta bu'i steng na gzhal med khang ri rab kyi steng brgyad kyi khyon yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:4442: de ltar gzhal yas khang re re na 'dod pa na spyod pa lha'i bu dang /
NK104(phe)001:4443: bu mo bye ma phrag drug khri drug khri'i sprul pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4444: longs spyod du mar snang ba 'phrul pa 'ba' zhig la spyod pa las med /
NK104(phe)001:4445: sdug bsngal du lo stong phrag re re la dran
NK104(phe)001:4446: pa skad cig tsam las ltung ba dran pa las
NK104(phe)001:4447: med do // zas dang gos mi dgos te /
NK104(phe)001:4448: bu dang bu mo skyed pa dang zas dang dga' bar sprul pa rang chas /
NK104(phe)001:4450: snang ba bdud rtsir mthong bas zas skoms thams cad dus gcig la nges par thob bo //
NK104(phe)001:4452: gzhan gyi sprul pa'i bye brag du ma la rab tu dga' ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4453: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lus khru sum brgya nyi shu /
NK104(phe)001:4456: gnas rab tu smon pa dang ldan pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4457: nyon mongs pa rags pa med pa /
NK104(phe)001:4458: rin po che 'ching bu'i bye mas bdal ba las /
NK104(phe)001:4459: dal zhing 'jam pa'i mdangs yod pa'i steng /
NK104(phe)001:4460: gzhal med khang ri rab kyi steng bcu drug gi khyon yod pa na /
NK104(phe)001:4461: lha'i rol mo mi 'dra ba dgu phrag dgu stong lnga brgya lnga 'byung bar byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4462: longs spyod gzhan gyi sprul pa la dbang byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4464: 'di yan chad na zas dang gos dngos su dgos pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:4465: snang ba khrus kyi rdzing bu dal zhing 'jam pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4466: lha'i rol mo sna tshogs par snang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:4468: gzhan gyis sprul pa'i las sna tshogs pa la sprul par byed pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4470: de dag la 'dod khams su 'dogs pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4471: 'dod chags dngos su gnyis la spyod pas na 'dod khams zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4472: gzugs khams gnas rigs bcu bdun ni /
NK104(phe)001:4474: 'di la lus dngos su med pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4475: rig byed 'od kyi lus su yod la /
NK104(phe)001:4476: 'dod chags bltas pas tshim pas chog pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4477: skye ba yang rdzus nas skye ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4478: de bzhin du longs spyod la sogs pas khyad par byas so //
NK104(phe)001:4479: de dag gi ming ni tshangs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4496: de la tshangs pa'i lus tshad ni /
NK104(phe)001:4498: 'od khru bzhi tshe bye ba cig dang 'bum phrag drug /
NK104(phe)001:4499: gnas rab tu dge ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:4501: lus sems pa'i gnas kyis bde ba rgyas pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4502: sa gzhi thams cad pad ma rab tu 'od 'phro ba las mi 'da' ba'i steng /
NK104(phe)001:4503: gzhal med khang stong dang po'i lo gang dang mnyam pa /
NK104(phe)001:4504: rin po che 'bum phrag brgyad kyi rgyu las byung ba /
NK104(phe)001:4505: de dag re re la lha dang lha mo bye
NK104(phe)001:4506: ba phrag bdun stong bdun stong 'char bar byed pa'i
NK104(phe)001:4507: gnas so // longsa glu gar dang rtse 'jo la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4508: ltung ba 'dod lha nas rim gyis so //
NK104(phe)001:4509: snang ba 'dod yon dga' ba la spyod do //
NK104(phe)001:4510: tshangs pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4511: 'di yan chad bsod nams kyi las kyis tshangs pas /
NK104(phe)001:4512: nyon mongs pa khong khro med do //
NK104(phe)001:4513: 'dod pa la tshangs pas na tshangs pa zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4514: tshangs ris kyi lus kyi tshad ni /
NK104(phe)001:4515: khru nyis brgya zhe brgyad pa /
NK104(phe)001:4517: tshe lo bye ba gsum dang /
NK104(phe)001:4519: gnas rab tu mdzes par bkod pa /
NK104(phe)001:4521: rin po che'i rigs mi 'dra ba'i sil ma dpag
NK104(phe)001:4522: tu med pas shin tu spras par bkod pa'i steng
NK104(phe)001:4523: na / gzhal med khang stong gnyis pa'i lo ka dang mnyam pa /
NK104(phe)001:4524: rin po che grangs med pa'i rgyu las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4525: lha dang lha mo bye ba phrag khrig cig dang stong phrag bzhi bzhir 'char bar byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4526: longs spyod nyin mtshan du lha'i 'dod yon la spyod do /
NK104(phe)001:4528: snang ba bde ba rtog bcas la spyod cing snang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:4529: tshangs ris zhes bya ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4530: lus dang yan lag dang sngon tshangs par spyad pa'i ris yod pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4532: tshangs pa mdun na 'don gyi lus kyi tshad rgyang grags cig /'od rang gi 'dom bzhir gsal ba /
NK104(phe)001:4533: tshe lo bye ba drug dang /
NK104(phe)001:4534: 'bum phrag bzhi gnas brgyad pa g.yo ba med pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4535: der skyes tshad la rnam par rtog pa las kyi rlung brgyad kyis g.yo bar mi nus so //
NK104(phe)001:4536: de lta bu'i steng na gzhal med khang rin po che bye ba phrag mang po las byung ba /
NK104(phe)001:4537: stong gsum gyi stong dang mnyam pa /
NK104(phe)001:4538: lha dang lha mo gong ma las log 'gyur ro //
NK104(phe)001:4539: longs spyod rtag tu sgyu ma pa mig yengs pa'i rnam pa tsam la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4540: ltung ba gong ma nas 'og ma 'og mar ltung bar byed do //
NK104(phe)001:4541: snang ba mchod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs par mthong ngo //
NK104(phe)001:4542: tshangs pa mdun na 'don zhes bya ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4543: lha de dag re re'i mdun na lha phran kha thon byed pa re re 'don pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4545: 'od chung gi lus kyi tshad rgyang grags gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4546: 'od kyi rgyang grags gcig tu gsal ba /
NK104(phe)001:4547: gnas bde ba skyob pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4548: khyad par gyi rlung gi bde bas gzhal med khang nam mkha' las bskyod par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4549: de'i steng na gzhal med khang stong gsum gyi stong gnyis 'gyur tsam /
NK104(phe)001:4550: rin po che bsam gyis mi khyab pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4551: 'di yan chad tshe skal par thub pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4552: tshangs pa'i lha gsum po ni 'dod pa dang brten
NK104(phe)001:4553: 'di ni 'dod pa las rings pas skal pa chen
NK104(phe)001:4555: longs spyod 'di la yengs nas nyin mtshan mi phyed do //
NK104(phe)001:4556: snang ba ni reg bya bde bar snang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:4558: rang gi lus la 'od rgyang grags gcig gis chung bas 'od chung zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4559: 'od gsal la lus rgyang grags bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4562: gnas yang pa can zhes bya ba nam mkha'i mthas thug pa /
NK104(phe)001:4563: gzhal med khang stong gsum bzhi 'gyur rin po che rab tu rgyas pa las grub pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4564: longs spyod rtag tu bde bas myos pa /
NK104(phe)001:4565: snang ba yid tshim par snang ba /
NK104(phe)001:4567: gzhal yas khang tsam gcig gi nang 'od kyi khengs par byed pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4569: tshad med kyi lus rgyang grags brgyad /
NK104(phe)001:4572: gnas sems yangs pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4573: der phyin pa tsam gyis sems kyi bsam gtan skye ba /
NK104(phe)001:4574: gzhal med khang stong gsum brgyad 'gyur ro //
NK104(phe)001:4575: longs spyod 'dod pa dam pas chog mi shes pa /
NK104(phe)001:4576: snang ba rab tu yi rangs pa las spyod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4578: 'od gzhal yas khang las thal nas snang bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4580: dge chung gi lus dpag tshad gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4581: 'od gcig gis gnas rnams gsal bar byed pa tshe bskal pa bcu gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4583: gzhal med khang stong gsum bcu drug 'gyur /
NK104(phe)001:4584: longs spyod ltas pas chog mi shes pa /
NK104(phe)001:4585: snang ba bde ba dang yangs par spyod pa /
NK104(phe)001:4586: dge chung zhes bya ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4587: thog ma dge ba chung ba las smin pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4589: dge rgyas kyi lus tshad dpag tshad bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4591: tshe bskal pa sum cu rtsa gnyis gnas pa dad dang ldan pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4592: dri zhim pa sna tshogs snang bar byed pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4593: gzhal yas khang stong gsum sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi khyon /
NK104(phe)001:4594: longs spyod sems tshim pas bde ba /
NK104(phe)001:4595: snang ba dge ba bcu 'ba' zhig la spyod pas na dge rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4596: tshad med dge lus dpag tshad brgyad /
NK104(phe)001:4598: tshe bskal pa drug cu rtsa gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4599: gnas rnam par mdzes pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4600: rin po che rab tu spel legs pa'i phreng ba dkar dmar gyis spras pa'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4601: gzhal yas khang stong gsum gyi stong drug cu rtsa gnyis kyi khyon /
NK104(phe)001:4602: longs spyod lta bas chog mi shes pa snang ba
NK104(phe)001:4603: sdig pa'i snang ba skad cig kyang mi skye bas
NK104(phe)001:4604: na tshad med dge zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4605: sprin med 'od kyi lus dpag tshad bcu drug /'od gnas brgyad 'gyur /
NK104(phe)001:4606: tshe bskal pa brgyad dang nyer bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4607: gnas sprin dang bral ba zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4608: 'byung ba sprin mi snang ba'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4609: gzhal med stong gsum nyer bzhi'i khyon /
NK104(phe)001:4610: longs spyod gang la yang reg pa'i gnas bde ba /
NK104(phe)001:4611: snang ba rin po che'i phung po rab tu mched par mthong bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4613: bsod nams skyes lus dpag tshad sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4615: tshe bskal pa nyis brgya bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK104(phe)001:4616: gnas rab tu 'jam pa dang ldan pa zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:4617: gang reg pa 'jam pa'i bde ba nyams su myong bar 'gyur ba'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4618: gzhal med khang stong gsum brgya bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad kyi khyon yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:4619: longs spyod gzhal du med pa /
NK104(phe)001:4620: snang ba gang la yang yid mi 'jug pas na bsod nams skyes zhes /
NK104(phe)001:4621: las khyad par can bsags pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4622: 'bras bu che ba'i lus kyi tshad dpag tshad drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4623: 'od gnas sum cu rtsa gnyis su gsal /
NK104(phe)001:4624: tshe bskal pa bzhi brgya dgu bcu rtsa drug /
NK104(phe)001:4625: gnas rab tu bskyod pa dang bral ba zhes bya ba na /
NK104(phe)001:4626: stong gsum gyi stong bzhi brgya dgu bcu rtsa drug gi khyon gyi gzhal med khang yod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4627: longs spyod 'dod pas mi drel la /
NK104(phe)001:4628: snang ba 'bras bu thob pa 'ba' zhig tu snang bas na 'bras bu che ba zhes bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4629: 'og ma'i ltung ba'i du kha'i dran pa dang bral ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4630: mi che ba'i lus dpag tshad brgya nyer brgyad /
NK104(phe)001:4631: 'od gnas drug cu rtsa bzhir khyab par gnas /
NK104(phe)001:4632: tshe bskal pa dgu brgya dgu bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4633: gnas nam mkha'i mtha' la spyod pa zhes bya ba'i steng na /
NK104(phe)001:4634: gzhal med khang stong gsum dgu brgya dgu bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4635: longs spyod dpag par dka' ba /
NK104(phe)001:4636: snang ba dgra med pas na mi che ba zhes bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4637: lha 'di dag dpon g.yog med par gzugs mnyam pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4638: mi gdung ba'i lus dpag tshad nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa drug 'od gnas brgya nyer brgyad du snang /
NK104(phe)001:4639: tshe bskal pa stong dgu brgya bdun cu rtsa gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4640: gnas srid pa dang bral ba zhes bya ba na /
NK104(phe)001:4641: gzhal med khang stong gsum dgu brgya dgu bcu'i khyon /
NK104(phe)001:4642: longs spyod rangs pa dag pa la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4643: snang ba gang mthong ba tsam gyis gzhan gyi yid 'phrog pas na mi gdung ba zhes bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4644: de nyid kyi yid 'phrog kyang gdug sems mi skye bas na'o //
NK104(phe)001:4645: gya nom snang ba'i lus dpag tshad bzhi brgya dang
NK104(phe)001:4646: bcu gnyis 'od ga nas nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa
NK104(phe)001:4647: drug tu snang / tshe bskal pa sum stong dgu brgya bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK104(phe)001:4648: gnas 'dod pa rab tu zhi ba na /
NK104(phe)001:4649: gzhal med khang stong sum stong dgu brgya bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad kyi khyon /
NK104(phe)001:4650: longs spyod ldan par dga' ba la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4651: snang ba tshad du gzung du med par snang bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4653: 'di la 'og ma 'gran par mi bzod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4654: shin tu mthong ba'i lus dpag tshad nyer bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4655: 'od gnas lnga brgya dang bcu gnyis su gsal /
NK104(phe)001:4656: tshe bskal pa bdun stong brgya dgu bcu rtsa drug thub /
NK104(phe)001:4657: gnas 'jig pa dang bral ba zhes bya ba na /
NK104(phe)001:4658: gzhal med khang stong gsum bdun stong brgya dgu bcu rtsa drug gi khyon /
NK104(phe)001:4659: longs spyod sred pa mtha' yas pa la spyod /
NK104(phe)001:4660: snang ba gdung ba chod pas na shin tu mthong ba zhes bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4661: gang mthong ba tsam gyi dga' bde la spyod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4662: 'og min gyi lus dpag tshad nyis stong bzhi brgya /
NK104(phe)001:4663: 'od gnas stong dang nyer bzhi gsal /
NK104(phe)001:4664: tshe bskal pa khri phrag gcig dang lnga stong brgyad brgya dang bcu gnyis thub bo //
NK104(phe)001:4665: gnas ni rtse mo can zhes bya ba bsam gtan gyi mthar thug pa na /
NK104(phe)001:4666: gzhal yas khang re re la khri dang lnga stong dang brgya bcu gnyis bcu gnyis yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4667: longs spyod bsam pa dka' ba nyid la spyod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4668: snang ba mi 'phro bar snang bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4669: 'og min gyi lha zhes bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4670: gzugs kyi lha rnams kyi 'og min pas na 'og min no //
NK104(phe)001:4671: de ltar de dag gi tshad dang rim pa la sogs pa yod par cis shes na /
NK104(phe)001:4672: pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag brgya pa las /
NK104(phe)001:4673: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i lha rnams yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4674: sum cu rtsa gsum lha rnams yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4675: zhes pa la sogs pas shes so //
NK104(phe)001:4676: de yang dpag tshad brtsi ba la yang /
NK104(phe)001:4677: rdul phra rab bdun la lcags rdul gcig /
NK104(phe)001:4678: de bdun la chu rdul gcig /
NK104(phe)001:4679: de bdun la ri bong gi rdul gcig /
NK104(phe)001:4680: de bdun la lug rdul gcig /
NK104(phe)001:4681: de bdun la glang rdul gcig /
NK104(phe)001:4682: de bdun la skar khung gi nyi zer gcig de bdun la sro ma gcig /
NK104(phe)001:4684: de bzhi la nas gcig de bcu gnyis la mtho gang /
NK104(phe)001:4687: de lnga brgya la rgyang grags cig /
NK104(phe)001:4688: de brgyad la dpag tshad gcig go /
NK104(phe)001:4690: gling bzhi dang ri rab dang bcas pa gcig nas stong du bgrangs pa la stong dang po //
NK104(phe)001:4693: de dag ni gzugs khams so //
NK104(phe)001:4694: da ni gzugs med pa'i lha rnams te /
NK104(phe)001:4695: 'di dang gzugs khams kyi khyad par ni /
NK104(phe)001:4696: rig byed 'od kyi lus su yang med la /
NK104(phe)001:4697: skye ba shes pa tsam la mched pa snang ba tsam las med pas /
NK104(phe)001:4698: gzugs khams kyi khyad byas so //
NK104(phe)001:4699: gzugs khams man chad yod snang 'ba' zhig tu spyod la /
NK104(phe)001:4700: 'di na med snang 'ba' zhig tu spyod pas so //
NK104(phe)001:4701: 'di'i lus ni yid kyang med do //
NK104(phe)001:4702: shes pa stong lus su yod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4707: yon min med min gyi skye mched do //
NK104(phe)001:4708: de la nam mkha' mtha' yas kyi lus nam mkha' dang mnyam ste /
NK104(phe)001:4709: 'di la lus med pas 'du shes tsam las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:4711: de yang stong par rang dngas su yod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4712: gzhal yas kyang de tsam mo //
NK104(phe)001:4713: tshe bskal pa grangs med pa gcig thub /
NK104(phe)001:4714: ting nge 'dzin dmigs pa yengs mi srid pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4715: longs spyod tshad med pa snang ba nam mkha' dang mtshungs so /
NK104(phe)001:4716: snang ba nam mkha' ltar snang bas na nam mkha' mtha' yas pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4717: 'du shes nam mkha'i mtha' la yas pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4718: nam mkha' mtha' yas zhes de la brten nas bsam gtan skye la /
NK104(phe)001:4719: mched pa tshe zad pa'i dus na ltung ba dran pa las med do //
NK104(phe)001:4720: rnam shes mtha' yas kyi lus rnam par shes pas gang du khyab pa /
NK104(phe)001:4723: 'di ni rnam par shes pa las med pas so //
NK104(phe)001:4724: tshe bskal pa grangs med pa gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4725: ting nge 'dzin dmigs pa rtse gcig longs spyod yod
NK104(phe)001:4726: pa dang med pa rnam shes tsam du ma dmigs
NK104(phe)001:4727: / snang ba rnam par shes pa tsam du snang bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4728: rnam shes mtha' yas zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4729: de yang skye ba rnam par mched pas shes pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4730: cung zad med pa'i lus med pa'i mthas gtugs pa /
NK104(phe)001:4731: 'od dang gzhal yas kyang de dang mnyam ste /
NK104(phe)001:4732: 'di ni med pa blo'i yul du song bas so //
NK104(phe)001:4733: tshe bskal pa grangs med pa bzhi /
NK104(phe)001:4734: ting nge 'dzin dmigs pa cir yang med pa /
NK104(phe)001:4735: longs spyod med pa'i nor la yengs pa /
NK104(phe)001:4736: snang ba cung zad tsam yang med par mthong bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4739: mched pa med pas ngoms te tshe zad pa'i ltung ba dran pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4740: yod min med min gyi lus yod pas nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pas /
NK104(phe)001:4741: med pas stong pa nyid bsam ngor yod med du mi snang ba /
NK104(phe)001:4742: 'od dang gzhal yas kyang de tsam mo //
NK104(phe)001:4743: tshe bskal pa grangs med brgyad do /
NK104(phe)001:4744: ting nge 'dzin yod med kyi mthar mi 'dzin pa /
NK104(phe)001:4745: longs spyod bsam tu med pa snang ba yod min
NK104(phe)001:4746: te stong sangs med min te 'gyur bar snang bas
NK104(phe)001:4747: na / yod min med min te /
NK104(phe)001:4748: skye ba yod pa rtog bcas /
NK104(phe)001:4749: mched pa yod min gyi mtha' ma rnyed pas /
NK104(phe)001:4750: tshe zad pas ltung ba dran pa na /
NK104(phe)001:4751: sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun la rgyab kyis bltas nas ngan song du 'phen par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4752: 'dod pa'i lha rnams kyi bsags pa'i khyad kyis gnas
NK104(phe)001:4753: re re la lus rigs mi 'dra ba tha dad
NK104(phe)001:4754: pa'o // gzugs ni rgyu bsod nams bsags par gcig pa'i phyiir gnas rigs bcu bdun du byung kyang /
NK104(phe)001:4755: gnas re re na rigs mi 'dra ba med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4756: gzugs med kyang ting nge 'dzin gcig pas shes pa
NK104(phe)001:4757: gcig las tha dad pa gnas re re las mi
NK104(phe)001:4758: rgyu ba'o // de yang skyes pa bardzusa skyes dang /
NK104(phe)001:4761: mngal skyes bzhi 'di dag rnams la ma tshangs pas
NK104(phe)001:4762: na skyes la gnas bye brag tu 'dod pa la
NK104(phe)001:4763: drug dang / gzugs bcu bdun dang /
NK104(phe)001:4765: spyi la gnas nyer bdun yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4766: dag par byed pa ni 'og le'u drug pa'i zhabs nas ston no //
NK104(phe)001:4767: de ltar 'dir 'gro ba mi'i gnas mi ston par lha ston pa ci zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:4768: thog ma lha nas 'gro ba mi rnams chad pas kyang sngon du lha bstan la /
NK104(phe)001:4769: tshe dang bsod nams kyi khyad kyis lha bstan pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4770: 'o na de ltar lha'i skye ba bstan pa la dgos pa ci yod ce na /
NK104(phe)001:4772: de dag gi gnas dang tshe dang 'od la sogs pa bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:4774: de nyid du mi 'jug pas khams gsum du ma zhugs pas sangs rgya ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK104(phe)001:4775: de'i phyir na 'di shes pas grol bas shes grol zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:4776: shes pas grol ba de yang /
NK104(phe)001:4777: dper na dug ngo shes pas /
NK104(phe)001:4779: ma zos pas dug gis 'chi mi srid pa bzhin no //
NK104(phe)001:4780: dug ngo ma shes pas zos nas 'chi ba bzhin
NK104(phe)001:4781: du lha'i gnas gzhan gyis mi shes pas khams gsum
NK104(phe)001:4782: du 'khor ba'o // 'dis lha'i gnas gzhan shes pas kho thag chod /
NK104(phe)001:4784: dper na lam log par phyin pa'i 'gro ba /
NK104(phe)001:4785: log par shes pas de nyid du phyis mi 'gro ba bzhin no //
NK104(phe)001:4786: des na 'gro ba'i gnas lugs shes pas 'gro ba drug gi 'khor lo la 'jug mi srid pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4788: 'gro ba drug gi las dang skye gnas shes nas /
NK104(phe)001:4789: srid pa'i 'khor lo rgyun chad do //
NK104(phe)001:4791: yang mdo sde las brgya pa las /
NK104(phe)001:4792: 'jig rten dga' bde'i bcud kyis bcings rnams las /
NK104(phe)001:4793: lha yi rigs rnams shes pas de la grol //
NK104(phe)001:4795: gser gyi mkha' lding gi rgyud las kyang /
NK104(phe)001:4796: gang gis rang rig ye shes par //
NK104(phe)001:4797: srid pa gsum du 'khyams pa la //
NK104(phe)001:4798: 'gro ba'ii gzugs dang kha dog ni //
NK104(phe)001:4799: shes pa tsam gyis grol bar nges //
NK104(phe)001:4800: zhes pa la sogs te lung drangs na bsam gyis mi khyab po //
NK104(phe)001:4801: de'i phyir na gnad shes pa tsam gyis grol ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4802: rgya nag po'i then mdud rang gis rang grol ba lta bu'o //
NK104(phe)001:4803: de yang gnad gang yin na /
NK104(phe)001:4804: 'gro ba drug gi skye gnas shes pa des //
NK104(phe)001:4805: so so'i bye brag shes pas de nyid grol ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4806: dper na sbrul gyi mdud pa sus kyang ma bkrol bar rang gis rang grol ba lta bu'o //
NK104(phe)001:4807: de'i phyir na rang ka ma rang gis rang grol ba ste /
NK104(phe)001:4808: dri mas dri ma dag par byed pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4809: lcags kyis lcags gcod pa dang 'dra bar /
NK104(phe)001:4810: rigs drug tu mi 'khor ba rigs drug gi mtshan
NK104(phe)001:4811: nyid gtan la phebs pa tsam gyis mi 'khor bar
NK104(phe)001:4812: nges pa'o // des na chos rnams kyang shes bya zer ba las rtogs bya'am /
NK104(phe)001:4814: brtags bya mi zer bas na /
NK104(phe)001:4815: shes pa tsam gyis grol bar gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:4819: don gyis snga phyi'i mtshams sbyor bar byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4820: yang na ngal bso lta bu'am /
NK104(phe)001:4822: yang na gong ma dang 'og ma'i bar yin la /
NK104(phe)001:4823: 'di ni khyad par du dang po gnyis pa'i bar la smos pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4824: ste ni lhag ma can nam /
NK104(phe)001:4825: ma smos pa sdud par byed pa'i tshig yin pas /
NK104(phe)001:4826: 'di la brten nas klong lhag ma lnga bstan par bya /
NK104(phe)001:4828: dang po ni thog mar smos pas /
NK104(phe)001:4831: rin po che gsal ba'i phreng ba las /
NK104(phe)001:4832: klong dang po gsal bar byas pa /
NK104(phe)001:4833: mkhas pa byi ma la mu tras mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK104(phe)001:4836: da ni klong gnyis pa chos nyid thams cad gtan
NK104(phe)001:4837: la phab pa'i klong gi tshig don rin po che
NK104(phe)001:4838: gsal ba'i phreng ba ltar bshad na /
NK104(phe)001:4839: de la klong gnyis pa chos nyid thams cad gtan la phab pa'i klong la gnyis te /
NK104(phe)001:4840: byang chub sems dpa' gnyis kyis chos nyid kyi go
NK104(phe)001:4841: ba bstun pa bka' bgro ba'i rang bzhin du bstan
NK104(phe)001:4842: pa dang / ston pa dang sdud pa po'i khyad par zhus pa dang lan btab pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4844: ston pas khyad par gyi ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK104(phe)001:4845: sems can gyi don la dgongs pa bstan pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4846: dran bsdur ba bka' bgro ba dngos bstan pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4847: de la ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NK104(phe)001:4848: sems can gyi don la dgongs par bstan pa ni
NK104(phe)001:4849: / de nas ston pa kun tu bzang pos zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:4850: de nas ni klong dang po bshad pa ma thag pa nas /
NK104(phe)001:4851: ston pa ni yon tan la dmigs te bos pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4852: kun tu 'dus shing ma lus pa la /
NK104(phe)001:4853: bzang pos ni yon tan gyi gzhir gyur nas skyon dang dri ma mi mnga' ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4854: chos thams cad ni 'khor ba'i dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos so //
NK104(phe)001:4855: mnyam pa nyid ni matha'i rnam par rtog pa thams cad las grol nas /
NK104(phe)001:4856: gang du'ang mi 'byed rnam par rol pa la gnyis med du gnas pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4857: gnyis su med pa ni 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad snang stong gang du'ang mi 'byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4858: ting nge 'dzin dus thams cad du mnyam pa'i don las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4859: gnyis med ni bdag yul dngos 'dzin /
NK104(phe)001:4860: rdo rje snying po bya ba la skye 'jig med
NK104(phe)001:4861: pa'i chos nyid dwangs ma thams cad bsdus pa zhes
NK104(phe)001:4862: bya'o // snyoms par zhugs so zhes pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4863: 'khor 'das gang du'ang ma phye ba'i don //
NK104(phe)001:4864: don rab tu snang ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:4865: sems can las dmigs pa'i khyad par las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4866: zhes ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK104(phe)001:4867: sems can gyi don la dgongs par bstan pa nas /
NK104(phe)001:4868: da ni byang chub sems dpa' gnyis kyis bka' bgro ba dngos bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:4869: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:4870: de nas ni ston pa ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs pas mthong ba de nas zhes bya la /
NK104(phe)001:4871: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'od zer
NK104(phe)001:4872: kun 'dus gyis ni klong dang po'i sdud pa po'i
NK104(phe)001:4873: ming ngo // 'khor ni ston pa'i tha dad du
NK104(phe)001:4874: 'dus pa de dag rnams la ni byang chub sems
NK104(phe)001:4875: dpa' dpag tu med pa 'dus la bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:4876: bcom la sogs pa'i tshig gsum gzhung gis shes so //
NK104(phe)001:4877: 'khor de dag ni byang chub sems dpa' lag na rdo rje dang /
NK104(phe)001:4881: blo gros mi zad pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4882: sa'i snying po la sogs pa'i bye ba khrag khrig rnams kyi nang nas /
NK104(phe)001:4883: byang ba las dang nyon mongs pa dri ma byang la /
NK104(phe)001:4884: chub pa tshogs rnam pa gnyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4885: sems dpa' chen po bdag gzhan gyi don la chos thams cad du sems dpa' las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:4886: glog ni 'od zer kun nas sprin dang bral bas zhes bya bas ni /
NK104(phe)001:4887: glog gi 'od zer sdud pa po'i ming yin la /
NK104(phe)001:4888: 'di skad du tshig tu brjod do ni bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK104(phe)001:4889: kye kye ston pa kun tu bzang po'i 'khor du 'dus pa'i sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK104(phe)001:4890: rdo rje mi bskyod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4894: de dag gi yum la sogs pa longs sku rnams dang /
NK104(phe)001:4895: byang chub sems dpa' lag na rdo rje la sogs pa dpag tu med pa rnams dang /
NK104(phe)001:4896: gzhan yang lo ka'i 'khor lha dang mi dang lha ma yin dang /
NK104(phe)001:4899: mi ma yin pa'i gzugs 'dzin pa dpag tu med rnams nyon cig ces bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:4900: chos kyi sku'i ston pa dpal kun tu bzang po ni ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4907: so so'i bye brag gi mtshan nyid do //
NK104(phe)001:4909: rten pa'i las khyad par can bsgrub cing gzhan gyi las dang /
NK104(phe)001:4910: spyod pa sgyur bar byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4911: nges tshig ni tha mal pa las zlog nas lus
NK104(phe)001:4912: ngag yid snga ma las gnas 'gyur zhing chos pas
NK104(phe)001:4913: na chos so // dbye ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:4917: de las 'di ni 'khor ba las mthar 'byin par byed pas na mthar 'byin pa'i chos so //
NK104(phe)001:4918: de yang khyad par du phye na /
NK104(phe)001:4923: phyin ci log gi chos so //
NK104(phe)001:4924: sor gzhag pa ni lha dang mi lung du ma bstan pa rnams so //
NK104(phe)001:4925: phyin ci log ni mu stegs kyi lta ngan sum brgya dang drug cu la sogs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4926: 'das pa ni gong ma'i gsum po la bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:4927: bstan pa'i chos gsung rabs yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:4928: lam gyi chos 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad dang /
NK104(phe)001:4929: bsgrub pa'i chos mdo sde bcu gnyis so //
NK104(phe)001:4930: chos kyi byed pa'i las ni /
NK104(phe)001:4932: bde ba sdug pa btang snyoms su byed la /
NK104(phe)001:4933: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos bde ba skyed par byed de //
NK104(phe)001:4934: de yang 'khor ba las thar bar byed do //
NK104(phe)001:4935: so so'i bye brag gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK104(phe)001:4936: 'khor ba'i chos kyi mtshan nyid sdug bsngal ba /
NK104(phe)001:4937: myang 'das kyi chos kyi mtshan nyid bde ba skyed par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4938: de lta bu'i chos 'khor 'das thams cad mnyam pa nyid ni /
NK104(phe)001:4939: yod med rtag chad snang stong gang du'ang ma grub pas na /
NK104(phe)001:4940: de nyid la ye nas nyon mongs kyi rdul dang /
NK104(phe)001:4941: 'byung ba'i rdul dang bral bar mkhyen pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:4942: byang chub sems dpa' glog gi 'od zer kun nas sprin dang bral bas /
NK104(phe)001:4944: de nas 'od zer kun 'dus kyis gsol pa /
NK104(phe)001:4945: byang chub sems dpa' mnyam pa nyid ces bya ba de ni don ci zhig ces dris so //
NK104(phe)001:4946: glog gi 'od zer kun nas sprin dang bral bas smras pas /
NK104(phe)001:4947: 'khor ba dang 'das pa'i chos thams cad snang ba
NK104(phe)001:4948: dang stong pa la sogs pa mnyam pa nyid ye
NK104(phe)001:4949: gdod ma nas / nyon mongs pa dang 'byung ba
NK104(phe)001:4950: phra rags kyi rdul dang bral ba zhes bya ba
NK104(phe)001:4951: gdod ma nas / ni / rtag pa mthar 'dzin pas rang rgyud du 'dzin pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4952: chad pa rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4953: rdul phra rab la don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4954: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4955: kun btags bkag nas gzhan dbang la don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4956: don dam dang kun rdzob la rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4957: sa dang lam don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4958: khrus dang gtsang sbra la don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4959: lta spyod ya bral ba la don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4960: lha dang dkyil 'khor la don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4961: lha dang lha mo'i dal la don dam du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang /
NK104(phe)001:4962: dbyings dang ye shes la don dam par 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang bral zhing /
NK104(phe)001:4963: dbang po dang yul la tha dad du 'dzin pa'i
NK104(phe)001:4964: rnam par rtog pa'i dri ma'i las dang sems 'ching
NK104(phe)001:4967: 'od zer kun 'dus gyis yang gsol ba /
NK104(phe)001:4968: de nyid kyi mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing rnam
NK104(phe)001:4969: par rtog pa'i dri ma med pa de gang yin
NK104(phe)001:4970: zhes dris pas / glog gi 'od zer kun nas sprin dang bral bas smras pa /
NK104(phe)001:4971: de ni tshig gis brjod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4972: sgra ji bzhin pa'i brjod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:4973: blo'i rnam par rtog pa'i brjod pa thams cad chos nyid kyi ngang du nye bar zhi ba ste /
NK104(phe)001:4974: de ji ltar zhi ba'i tshe na rnal 'byor pa
NK104(phe)001:4975: de'i blo yul dang yul can gang la'ang mi 'jug
NK104(phe)001:4977: yang gsol ba de ni phyi'i spros pa gcad pa tsam las ma gtogs pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:4978: rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi dgongs pa ni ma yin snyam nas /
NK104(phe)001:4979: de ji lta bu zhes dris pas /
NK104(phe)001:4981: de ma go na du ma dang tha snyad dang cha shas dang /
NK104(phe)001:4982: spros pa med pa nyag gcig zla med pas /
NK104(phe)001:4985: mtshan ma'i spros pa thams cad bral ba'o zhes smras pas /
NK104(phe)001:4986: don thog tu phebs nas de de bzhin du dngos
NK104(phe)001:4987: po gshis kyi 'dug tshul la gang gis kyang sgros
NK104(phe)001:4988: ma btags pas / rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi dgongs pa yin no //
NK104(phe)001:4989: de ltar chos thams cad nga la yang klong dang
NK104(phe)001:4990: por ston pa kun tu bzang pos bstan pa yin
NK104(phe)001:4991: pas / da ltar yang byang chub sems dpa' khyod
NK104(phe)001:4992: kyis de ltar go ba ni shin tu legs so
NK104(phe)001:4993: pas / // zhes legs par byin nas zhes smras so //
NK104(phe)001:4994: zhes spyi don dang po byang chub sems dpa' gnyis
NK104(phe)001:4995: kyi chos nyid kyi dran pa bstun pa bka' bgro
NK104(phe)001:4996: ba rang bzhin bstan pa la gnyis su byas nas
NK104(phe)001:4997: bstan no // da ni spyi don gnyis pa ston
NK104(phe)001:4998: pa dang sdud pa'i khyad par zhus pa dang lan
NK104(phe)001:5000: rnal 'byor gyi bslab bya khyad par gyi chos spyod bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:5001: thabs kyi rang bzhin chos nyid rang gi ngo bo dang bsre bar bstan pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5002: skal pa bzang po'i gang zag pa la chos nyid don ji ltar skye ba bstan pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5003: 'dra gzhi khyad par gyi tshig gis rtsol ba dang bcas pa la bzla bar bstan pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:5004: de la rnal 'byor gyi bslab bya khyad par gyi
NK104(phe)001:5005: chos spyod bstan pa la nang don lngas bstan pa'i
NK104(phe)001:5006: dang po / ston pa la lung bstan pa'i rtogs pa'i yan lag rdzogs par bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:5007: de dag gis glengs pa ston pa kun tu bzang po la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:5008: mi rtog pa'i ngang las gsan nas ni gong ma'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs pa'i dus na'o //
NK104(phe)001:5009: lhag ma'i tshig gnyis gzhung na gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:5010: kye byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po glog
NK104(phe)001:5011: gi 'od zer kun nas sprin dang bral ba la
NK104(phe)001:5012: bos nas / byang chub sems dpa' 'od zer kun
NK104(phe)001:5013: nas 'dus bas kyang ngas klong dang po bstan pas
NK104(phe)001:5014: bos nas / / chos thams cad kyi don de ltar khong du chud pas de'i tshe na /
NK104(phe)001:5015: lus ngag yid mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob ste /
NK104(phe)001:5016: phyir mi ldog pa rang gi rig pa nyid la mngon par mig gi dbang po dag pas /
NK104(phe)001:5017: yul nam mkha' dag pa la gzigs pa /
NK104(phe)001:5019: dbyings dang rig pa 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa rnyed pa yin no //
NK104(phe)001:5020: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK104(phe)001:5021: po glog gi 'od zer kun nas sprin dang bral
NK104(phe)001:5022: ba khyod kyis kyang chos thams cad spros pa med
NK104(phe)001:5023: par go zhing / tshig tu shes nas lta ba
NK104(phe)001:5024: mngon sum du rtogs pa de shin tu legs so
NK104(phe)001:5025: par go zhing / // zhes spro ba bskyed nas /
NK104(phe)001:5026: chos kyi sku'i ston pa kun tu bzang po ngas
NK104(phe)001:5027: kyang byang chub sems dpa' khyod la 'khrul ba dang
NK104(phe)001:5029: ma 'khrul pa'i chos nyid ka nas dag pa'i snang
NK104(phe)001:5030: ba rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi tshig rnams spro
NK104(phe)001:5031: yis / byang chub sems dpa' khyod dad pa'i dbang
NK104(phe)001:5032: po phyin ci ma log pa thang lhod med pa
NK104(phe)001:5033: yis / dang / shes rab rang rgyud kyis bcings pa ma yin pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5034: lus ngag khyad par du mos gus dang ldan pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5035: sgo lnga'i dbang po yul gzhan la ma yengs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5036: sems rnam par rtog pa tha dad pas ma g.yengs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5037: blo mi dge ba'i phyogs su ma song ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:5038: rna ba'i dbang po sgra gzhan gyis bar ma chod
NK104(phe)001:5039: par nyon cig ces sngon 'byung du sdud pa po
NK104(phe)001:5040: la gdams pa'o // rjes 'jug gi dus na bla mas slob ma la gdams pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:5041: de yang 'das pa nas da ltar du rgyud dag /
NK104(phe)001:5042: da ltar nas ma 'ongs pa'i dus su rgyud dag pa'i gzhi gnas dang /
NK104(phe)001:5043: mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes gnyis mnga' bas na
NK104(phe)001:5044: rdo rje 'chang ba chen pos ni dus gsum du
NK104(phe)001:5045: 'du 'bral med par mnga' ba la bya /
NK104(phe)001:5046: de lta bu'i gzhi ka dag gi rtsal yon tan
NK104(phe)001:5047: du shar ba de yang nga kun tu bzang po
NK104(phe)001:5048: // sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams ye shes kyi nyi
NK104(phe)001:5049: ma stong gis rab tu brgyan pa'i tshad 'od dang
NK104(phe)001:5050: 'od zer rab tu brgyan pa tshad med pa zhes
NK104(phe)001:5051: // bya ba na / yod pa'i dus nga la des lung bstan pa /
NK104(phe)001:5052: mtha' gang la yang mi gnas pa'i chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa /
NK104(phe)001:5053: skye 'jig gang yang mi mnga' ba /
NK104(phe)001:5054: ka nas dag pa de la rnam par rtog pa
NK104(phe)001:5055: gang yang mi gnas pa'i ngo bo ka dag gi
NK104(phe)001:5057: ye thog ma nas rnam par dag pa'i tshe zhes dus khyad par can la dgongs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:5058: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sna tshogs dang /
NK104(phe)001:5059: 'das pa'i chos bde ba sna tshogs pa 'byin par byed pa'i rgyu rkyen dang bcas pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5064: ngo bo ni gnas shing rgya che ba la bya la /
NK104(phe)001:5065: nges tshig ni bcud 'dzin par byed cing mi gtong ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:5066: don gyis res khengs pa res stongs pa la bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:5068: ming gi snod gang la ming yod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5069: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis ka skyed par byed pa'i snod lus dang /
NK104(phe)001:5070: sems can rnams 'dzin cing mi gtong ba'i snod phyi'i lo ka ste /
NK104(phe)001:5072: mkha' la rlung brten de la chu yi phung po brten //
NK104(phe)001:5073: de la sa chen 'di brten de la 'gro ba brten //
NK104(phe)001:5075: de yang nam mkha' stong pa ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5076: rnam par 'dzin par byed pa zhes bya ba'i rlung
NK104(phe)001:5077: shin tu phra ba gser sa 'og tu bcug pa'i
NK104(phe)001:5079: g.yo byed rlung gi sa bon kha dog ljang khu 'od sna tshogs su 'phros pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5080: phyogs kun nas rlangs pa'i rnam pa lta bu'am /
NK104(phe)001:5081: na bun gyi rnam pa lta bu bun gyis langs pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5082: rnam par srub pa byed pa'i rlung zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:5083: gser gyi rdo rje lta bu'i dbyibs /
NK104(phe)001:5085: rab tu sra zhing brtan pa /
NK104(phe)001:5086: nus pa dang stobs rab tu che ba //
NK104(phe)001:5088: gang la thogs pa med pa zhig 'byung ste /
NK104(phe)001:5089: des gong ma'i na bun nam rlangs pa'i rnam pa lta bu de lan gcig dkrugs pas /
NK104(phe)001:5090: de rnams tshan pa dang dum bur chad par gyur nas /
NK104(phe)001:5091: phyogs kun tu long long du song ba rnam par sdud par byed pa'i rlung zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:5092: dbyibs lcags kyu'i rnam pa dang 'dra ba /
NK104(phe)001:5093: kha dog dkar po lnga tshad nyungs 'bru tshad nyis 'gyur /
NK104(phe)001:5094: rab tu khyab cing 'jug pa la mkhas pa /
NK104(phe)001:5095: 'dzin pa gcig gis lan cig 'phros pas bsdus te /
NK104(phe)001:5097: snga ma bas mthug cing brtan pa rgya mi che ba gcig tu byas so //
NK104(phe)001:5098: de nas 'phen par byed par byed pa ces bya ba'i rlung /
NK104(phe)001:5101: rab tu 'bar ba'i sgra yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5102: 'phar zhing mched pa'i stobs yod pa gcig /
NK104(phe)001:5103: snga ma de'i dbus nas langs pas /
NK104(phe)001:5104: du ba'i rnam pa ltar rab tu sngo zhing phyur ba langs pas /
NK104(phe)001:5105: me byung ste rab tu mched pas rlung gi dal de snga ma bas rgya che ba /
NK104(phe)001:5106: rngams mthug pa gcig tu byas so //
NK104(phe)001:5107: de nas yang brtan zhing bskyod pa'i rlung zhes bya ba /
NK104(phe)001:5108: dbyibs sna tshogs rdo rje lta bu /
NK104(phe)001:5109: kha dog ljang gu tshad rgya dang khyon dpag tu med pa /
NK104(phe)001:5110: rlung bzhi'i las rdzogs pas na /
NK104(phe)001:5112: 'dzin pa'i stobs kyis nam mkha' la 'thung nas mi gtong ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:5113: sdud pa'i stobs kyis yas su mi 'jug pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5114: mched cing 'phen pa'i stobs kyis phyir 'phel bar byed pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5115: yang zhing g.yo ba dang brtan pa gsum 'dus pa'i
NK104(phe)001:5116: stobs kyis brtan cing thur du mi 'phul ba dang
NK104(phe)001:5118: phan tshun du 'thor du mi 'jug pa'i las byed pas na /
NK104(phe)001:5119: sna tshogs rdo rje nam mkha' la lan gcig 'phar bas /
NK104(phe)001:5120: rngams dpag tshad bsam gyis mi khyab par rab tu brtan par byas /
NK104(phe)001:5121: de lan cig sa la thim pas rgya dpag tshad bsam gyis mi khyab pa sangs par byas /
NK104(phe)001:5122: de nas phyogs kun 'khor ba las rlung gi lha
NK104(phe)001:5123: mo bzhi rdo rje'i rwa bzhi nas 'degs pa'i stobs
NK104(phe)001:5124: byed pa gcig tu byas pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:5125: sus kyang byas pa med par rang byung du byung bas na 'byung ba zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:5126: de ltar na rlung gi dal de yang khod snyoms shing rgya che la rngams mthug pa /
NK104(phe)001:5127: bar snang la na bun 'khrigs pa'i rnam pa dang 'dra bar 'khrigs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:5128: de yang sems can gyi spyi mthun gyi las byung ba lta bu ni ma yin te /
NK104(phe)001:5129: rang 'byung du byung bas na 'byung ba zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:5131: 'byung ba chen po bcom ldan 'das zhes pas shes so //
NK104(phe)001:5132: de ltar kyang yun ring bar gnas pa las //
NK104(phe)001:5133: gong ma'i sdud par byed pa'i rlung la sogs pa bzhi po yang /
NK104(phe)001:5137: rlung gi rlung la sogs pa bzhi'i byed pa'i las so sor byed pa ste /
NK104(phe)001:5138: de ltar gnas pa'i rang bzhin las /
NK104(phe)001:5139: chu'i rlung sdud par byed pa lcags kyu'i rnam pa dang 'dra ba las /
NK104(phe)001:5140: rlan byi ba khra mo'i kha rlangs tsam las /
NK104(phe)001:5141: rmugs zil gyi rnam pa lta bur bun bun du snang ba las /
NK104(phe)001:5142: rlan gyi zil pa yod par dbyibs rab tu zlum pa /
NK104(phe)001:5144: rlung gi rtsal rdzogs pa las byung ba /
NK104(phe)001:5145: rlan cing sdud pa'i stobs yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5146: de las chu'i rlung rab tu khyab cing 'jug pas /
NK104(phe)001:5147: so so'i las kyi byed pa'i khyad par can zil
NK104(phe)001:5148: pa'i rnam pa lta bu las dang khyad par gyi
NK104(phe)001:5149: gzhi yod pa / kha dog dkar po dbyibs zlum po //
NK104(phe)001:5150: de nyid chu'i rang rtsal rdzogs pa las byung ba /
NK104(phe)001:5151: rab tu khod snyoms shing brtan pa'i stobs yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5152: des gong ma'i rmugs zil gyi rnam pa lta bu de /
NK104(phe)001:5153: lan cig gcig tu 'dres par byas pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5154: g.yo zhing bskyod pa'i las byas pas /
NK104(phe)001:5155: chu'i rang bzhin mer gyis chags par byas so //
NK104(phe)001:5156: de nas 'phel bar byed pa'i rlung chu'i me'i las ni /
NK104(phe)001:5158: kha dog rab tu dmar ba'i gdangs yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5159: rab tu 'bar ba'i sgra yod pa mched cing 'phel ba'i stobs yod pa gcig /
NK104(phe)001:5160: snga ma'i de'i dbus nas rlangs pa'i rnam pa dang 'dra ba langs pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5161: des snga ma de'i phyogs kun tu khyab pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5162: de'i las snga ma'i chu de lhog gis khol ba las /
NK104(phe)001:5163: phyogs thams cad nas chu'i sgra lhag lhag pa la sogs pa dpag tu med pa 'byung ngo //
NK104(phe)001:5164: de lan cig zhi ba las chu'i dal rgya khyon dpag tu med pa chags so //
NK104(phe)001:5165: de nas rnam par brtan pa'i chu /
NK104(phe)001:5170: 'o ma'i spris ma lta bu'i rgya chags pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5171: gyen la lan cig 'phar bas chu'i las rab tu brtan par bya ste /
NK104(phe)001:5172: 'byung ba bzhi'i las rdzogs pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5173: rngams mthug cing rgya che ba las /
NK104(phe)001:5174: chu'i dal dbyibs zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang ba
NK104(phe)001:5175: lta bu rab tu brtan pa rgya dang 'phang rab
NK104(phe)001:5176: tu sdug cing mched pa gcig tu chags so //
NK104(phe)001:5177: de la sdud pa'i stobs yod pas phan tshun gang du yang mi g.yo zhing mi dbyer bar byas /
NK104(phe)001:5178: rlan pa'i stobs yod pas thams cad chu'i rang bzhin du byas /
NK104(phe)001:5179: gsher pa'i stobs yod pas chu'i las rdzogs par byas so //
NK104(phe)001:5180: grang pa'i stobs kyis phan tshun mi 'pho bar byas pas gcig tu chags so //
NK104(phe)001:5181: de ltar kyang chu'i dal rgya che la rngams mthug la rgya che ba /
NK104(phe)001:5182: 'dzin par byed pa chu'i lha mo bzhis phyogs kun nas bzung bas /
NK104(phe)001:5183: gang du yang mi 'gyur bar byas pa /
NK104(phe)001:5184: de dag kyang rang 'byung du byung bas na 'byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:5186: mkha' la rlung brtan de chu'i phung po brtan //
NK104(phe)001:5190: sa'i rlung g.yo zhing brtan pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5192: de las rab tu rtsub pa'i las so sor phye ba las /
NK104(phe)001:5193: rdo rje rtse lnga pa rab tu srub cing 'phen pa'i thogs pa med pa gcig byung ste /
NK104(phe)001:5194: des phyi'i chu chen po de dag rnams lan cig dkrugs pas /
NK104(phe)001:5195: chu'i dal de rnams phyogs 'dres pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5196: dpag tshad lnga brgya tsam yan chad rab tu g.yos pas /
NK104(phe)001:5197: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i sgra byung ngo //
NK104(phe)001:5198: de lan cig chu'i steng rlung gi dal la thug
NK104(phe)001:5199: par lan cig thim pas de las chu'i dbyibs zlum
NK104(phe)001:5200: zhing gsal ba / kha dog dkar ba las 'od 'phros pas /
NK104(phe)001:5201: chu'i dal gyi mtha' nas rab tu bsdus pas /
NK104(phe)001:5202: yang gser gyi rdo rje lan gnyis su rlung gi dal la thug par dkrugs shing bskor bas /
NK104(phe)001:5203: chu'i dal kyang kha dog dkar po 'o ma'i rgya mtsho dang 'dra bar gyur pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:5204: de las rab tu rlangs pa las 'o ma las spris ma'i rnam pa dang 'dra bar gyur to //
NK104(phe)001:5205: de las kyi bye brag tha dad cing so sor mi g.yo bar byas so //
NK104(phe)001:5206: de nas sa'i ma kha dog dmar ba /
NK104(phe)001:5207: dbyibs chos kyi 'byung gnas dang 'dra ba /
NK104(phe)001:5208: gra gsum na spris ma sdud par byed pa'i rlung yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5209: des 'bar zhing mched pa'i stobs yod pa spris ma de lan cig bshig ste /
NK104(phe)001:5210: de'i stobs kyis gser gyi rdo rje de yang chu'i
NK104(phe)001:5211: dal la steng 'og tu lan gsum du dkrugs pas
NK104(phe)001:5212: / yar chu de dag kyang kha dog ser ba /
NK104(phe)001:5213: gser gyi khu ba lta bur gyur nas /
NK104(phe)001:5214: phyogs bzhi nas las kyi rlung gi lha mo shugs 'chang ma la sogs pa bzhin bus pas /
NK104(phe)001:5215: mtsho las dar chags pa'i rnam pa dang 'dra bar 'gyur te //
NK104(phe)001:5216: chab dron rnam pa lta bur gyur to //
NK104(phe)001:5217: de nas sa'i rang bzhin kha dog ser la /
NK104(phe)001:5218: dbyibs gru bzhi pa 'byung ba bzhi'i stobs yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5219: 'byung ba bzhi'i las rdzogs pa'i rtags su gru bzhi pa /
NK104(phe)001:5220: chu khyug 'khyags par byed pa'i stobs yod pa'i rtags su /
NK104(phe)001:5221: rab tu grang reg dang ldan pa /
NK104(phe)001:5222: de dang sa'i sa bon rdo rje dang gnyis 'dres pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5223: tsha ba me'i smin yod pas de las drod g.yos pas /
NK104(phe)001:5224: lan cig de bzhu bas zho rtsabs kyi rnam pa
NK104(phe)001:5225: ltar 'dres shing chu de dag kyang nur nur por
NK104(phe)001:5226: gyur / de la bskyod pa rlung gi stobs yod pas /
NK104(phe)001:5227: zho rtsabs dang 'dra ba'i gser gyi rdo rje des /
NK104(phe)001:5228: lan cig chu de rnams sprogs pas zhor chags pa ltar /
NK104(phe)001:5229: chu de rnams kyi steng du mi 'gul ba'i rtsi chags /
NK104(phe)001:5230: de nas lan gsum zho la srub kyis bsrubs pa ltar bsrubs pas /
NK104(phe)001:5231: chu la dar chags pa lta bu'i steng du gser gyi gzhi rab tu khod snyoms pa chags so //
NK104(phe)001:5232: de la grang ba chu'i sdud pa yod pa'i rtags su /
NK104(phe)001:5233: grang reg 'dus pa'i las kyi rlan gyis bsdus pas /
NK104(phe)001:5234: rab tu 'khrang zhing sra 'khregs dang ldan pa /
NK104(phe)001:5235: rgya khyon dpag tu med pa 'phang dang srid du mnyam par chags so //
NK104(phe)001:5236: de las 'byung ba so so'i las thad kar snang ba las /
NK104(phe)001:5237: sa de yang rab tu 'dar ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:5238: de las su sig pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5239: de nas rab tu 'khyoms pa las /
NK104(phe)001:5240: rin po che gser gyi dwangs ma rnams gcig tu bsdus las /
NK104(phe)001:5241: dbus su ri rab rin po che lnga las grub pa /
NK104(phe)001:5242: 'byung ba bzhi'i las rdzogs pa'i rtags su bang rim bzhi yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5243: sems can rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la spyod pa'i rtags su /
NK104(phe)001:5244: rin po che'i cog lnga dang bcas pa gcig chags so //
NK104(phe)001:5245: de yang bang rim gyi rming ni /
NK104(phe)001:5246: 'og ma gser gyi 'khor lo can dang /
NK104(phe)001:5247: rin po che rnam par bkod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:5248: spung rnam par 'dzin pa zhes bya ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:5249: mi sdug pa las grol ba'i bang rim yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:5250: tha ma 'jigs pa'i rtags su khong stong pa 'byung
NK104(phe)001:5251: ba bzhi las phyi nang kun grub pa'i rtags su
NK104(phe)001:5252: gru bzhi pa / dper na gser gyi man+dala g.ya' med pa'i steng du /
NK104(phe)001:5253: rin po che lnga bre kha sbub pa lta bu /
NK104(phe)001:5254: dpag tshad 'bum phrag gnyis dang bcas pa chags pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:5255: rang byung du byung bas na 'byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:5256: de nas gser gyi 'khor lo can gyi bang rim nas /
NK104(phe)001:5258: drod phebs pas dbus kyi ri bo nas dpag tshad lnga bcu'i phyogs bzhir gser gyi sa gzhi /
NK104(phe)001:5259: chab rim dang 'dra ba de bzhu ba las /
