NK104(phe)001:12118: lo ka'i gtam rgyud la grol zhes brjod pas kyang grol dgos te /
NK104(phe)001:12120: tshig de bcas pas grol na /
NK104(phe)001:12122: de la brten pa'i don gyis grol na /
NK104(phe)001:12123: shes pa dang ma shes pa ste snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK104(phe)001:12127: yod na rtag par yod pas shes sam /
NK104(phe)001:12128: mi rtag kyang shes pa la sogs pa gong ma dang 'dra'o //
NK104(phe)001:12129: don de gal te rtogs dgos na yang /
NK104(phe)001:12130: mtshan nyid dang ldan par rtogs na dngos por thal la /
NK104(phe)001:12131: mi ldan par rtogs na don ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12134: phyi ma la 'byung ba rang gnad dang bral nas grol zer ba dang khyad par med do //
NK104(phe)001:12135: gal te ma shes pa de ye nas grol lo
NK104(phe)001:12136: zhe na 'ang grol zhes rang 'dod pa'i sgras nyams
NK104(phe)001:12137: so // yang rdzogs pa chen po gnyen po las
NK104(phe)001:12138: 'das par smra ba rang grol du 'dod pa'i lugs
NK104(phe)001:12139: so // la ni / rang grol ba de rang thog nas grol lam /
NK104(phe)001:12140: rang gis rang grol snga ma ltar na rang thog nas rang grol na /
NK104(phe)001:12143: thug pa med pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro //
NK104(phe)001:12144: rang gi rang grol na'ang shes zhes gzhi la gzhag rang grol zhes yul yul can du 'gyur ro //
NK104(phe)001:12145: yang rdzogs pa chen po mthong ba rang dag par
NK104(phe)001:12146: grol bar smra ba cer grol du 'dod pa'i lugs
NK104(phe)001:12147: la brgal ba / de yang mthong ba tsam gyis grol lam /
NK104(phe)001:12148: mthong ba de shes pas grol /
NK104(phe)001:12150: mthong ba tsam gyis grol ba'i phyir /
NK104(phe)001:12151: mig gis gzugs mthong tshad grol lo /
NK104(phe)001:12154: med par shes pa la sogs pa snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK104(phe)001:12155: yang rdzogs pa chen po gzhi med du khas len
NK104(phe)001:12156: pa ye grol bar 'dod pa'i lugs la brgal ba
NK104(phe)001:12161: ma grol gyi sgras nyams la /
NK104(phe)001:12163: grol zhes grub pa med de ye nas grol na sems can mi rigs so //
NK104(phe)001:12164: bcos pa dang ma bcos pa'i sgra med do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12165: 'o na dngos pa'i gnas lugs la'ang grol ba dang
NK104(phe)001:12166: ma grol ba'i sgra med do zhes pas mgo basgre'o
NK104(phe)001:12167: // yang rdzogs pa chen po 'khor ba la thog
NK104(phe)001:12168: mtha' med par smra ba yod grol bar 'dod pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12170: 'di ltar snang ngo cog grol lam /
NK104(phe)001:12174: phyogs tsam grol na yongs kyi sgras nyams so //
NK104(phe)001:12175: 'byung ba rang gnad la thim nas grol na chad pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12176: de ma yin pa 'di ka ltar grol na /
NK104(phe)001:12178: 'di nyid rang grol ba yin no zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12179: theg pa che chung gi chos la dgos pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12180: de'i phyir na gzhi cir yang khas len pa 'di yang shes bya'i chos ma lags sam /
NK104(phe)001:12182: lan du ston pas sngar dang mtshungs zhes pas spros pa chod la /
NK104(phe)001:12183: nyams su blang bya'i chos ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12184: zhes bdun pa theg pa chen po 'dod pa rang
NK104(phe)001:12185: shar ba las cir yang khas blang du btub pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12186: brgal ba dris lan dang bcas pa bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:12187: da ni brgyad pa rdzogs pa chen po 'dod pa
NK104(phe)001:12188: rang shar ba las ka dag gi 'dod pa gzhan
NK104(phe)001:12189: skyon spang pa dris lan dang bcas pa bstan pa
NK104(phe)001:12190: ni / de nas byang chub sems dpa' yang /
NK104(phe)001:12191: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dgu gzhung na gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:12192: de nas ni gzhan 'dod sun phyung ba'i de nas
NK104(phe)001:12193: ston pas bka' dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul la
NK104(phe)001:12194: dgongs te / sdud pa po la rang 'dod bsgrub par rtsal ba /
NK104(phe)001:12195: kye ho sems dpa' chen po nyon cig ces bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:12196: ngas bstan pa'i tshig la 'khrul pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12197: sdud pa po khyod kyis tshig 'di dag legs par zung shig ces gdams te /
NK104(phe)001:12198: tshig gi spros pa tha snyad du ma'i spyod yul
NK104(phe)001:12199: ma yin pas tshig gis gtan la ma phebs pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12200: gnad do // mtshan ma'i spros pa yod med rtag chad du med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12201: cir yang snang ba ci'i ngo bor kyang grub pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12202: blo'i spros pa 'gyu ba sna tshogs pa med pas ngo bo la 'gyur ba med pa'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:12203: grub pa matha'i spros pa theg pa tha dad pa'i 'dod pa med pas chos med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12204: de 'ang tshig dang brjod pa las 'das pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12205: de ltar spros pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid ka
NK104(phe)001:12206: nas dag pa ni rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas
NK104(phe)001:12208: de la ming du btags na rang gi ngo bo rnam par dag pa snying po gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12209: de la tshig dang yi ge dang bral bas brjod pa las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12210: de la tshig gi brjod pas gtan la phab tu med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12211: mtshan nyid dang ngo bo sus kyang mi shes /
NK104(phe)001:12212: de'i rang bzhin la sgro 'dogs dang tha snyad kun dang bral te /
NK104(phe)001:12213: ye nas stong gsal dbyer mi phyed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12214: de'i thugs rje la gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i rnam par rtog pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12216: yul can rig pa'i ye shes su med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12217: de'i phyir na gzhi de las chos med pas chos kyi 'du shes tsam du'ang gzhi la med do //
NK104(phe)001:12218: de ltar ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje la gang
NK104(phe)001:12219: snang ba yul med cing yul dang rig pa'i ye
NK104(phe)001:12220: shes med / cir yang sems dang sems las byung
NK104(phe)001:12221: ba med pas khas len thams cad dang bral ba
NK104(phe)001:12222: shes med / zhes bya'o // de'i phyir na lung las kyang /
NK104(phe)001:12223: yod dang med pa 'di gnyis med pa'i chos yin te zhes pas so //
NK104(phe)001:12224: de ltar med pa'i snying po rang gi ngo bo la /
NK104(phe)001:12225: ci yang med yang sems can rnams kyi ngor byas nas re zhig tshig gi gtan la phab na /
NK104(phe)001:12226: rang gi ngo bo nyid ka dag la /
NK104(phe)001:12227: de'i 'char byed ma 'gags pa'i cha nas rang bzhin du ni lhun grub tu 'dod pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12228: re zhig tshig gi mtshon byed nyid de ltar te /
NK104(phe)001:12229: gnas lugs rang gi ngos nas gang gis kyang thog tu mi phebs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12230: ka dag ces pa'i gzhi la brgal ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:12231: byang chub sems dpa' nyi ma 'dus pa yis gsol ba /
NK104(phe)001:12232: ston pa kun tu bzang po lags /
NK104(phe)001:12233: gzhi de'i ngo bo nyid ni ka dag pa /
NK104(phe)001:12234: ma rig pa med pa'i cha nas ka dag gam rang bzhin rang la dag /
NK104(phe)001:12236: sems can 'byung bar mi rigs la /
NK104(phe)001:12237: 'og ma ltar na 'khor 'das kyi dmigs pa tha dad pa mi rigs so zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12238: ma rig pa zhes grub pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12239: ye dag chen po las bskyar gzhi med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12240: 'o na sems 'khrul pa 'di ci las byung zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12241: 'dug tshul la sems can grub pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12242: mngon sum gyis bsal lo zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12243: sems 'dug par mthong ngam grub pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12246: ka dag ma yin no zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12247: ka dag 'khrul pa yin par sus smra ste /
NK104(phe)001:12248: ka dag 'khrul pa ye nas dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:12249: de'ang rang bzhin gyis ka dag ces bya ba tsam du'ang grub pa med la /
NK104(phe)001:12250: ma dag bya ba tsam du'ang grub pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12251: dag dang ma dag med na lung bum bstan pa'i shes pa yin no zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12252: 'o na khyod kyis dag pa gang la zer /
NK104(phe)001:12254: chos nyid kyi dag byed khyod la blo la ma
NK104(phe)001:12255: grub pa blo sna tshogs su 'gyu ba'i phyir ro
NK104(phe)001:12256: // ma dag pa zhes gang yin /
NK104(phe)001:12257: 'khrul pa la zer na ma 'khrul pa la ltos pa'i 'khrul pa'am /
NK104(phe)001:12259: ma 'khrul pas ltos nas ma 'khrul pa'i mtshan nyid mi shes pas /
NK104(phe)001:12260: de ltar na sems can 'khor ba 'di mi rigs
NK104(phe)001:12261: zer ba la sems can shes bya la grub na
NK104(phe)001:12262: gang zag gis 'bad pa la dgos pa med do
NK104(phe)001:12263: // ma 'bad kyang rtsol ba med par rang grol ba'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:12264: sems can du snang ba cis shes na 'khrul pa'i shes pa 'dug pas shes zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12265: 'khrul pa khyod kyi blo la grub kyang shes bya la grub mi srid do //
NK104(phe)001:12266: ma rig pa'i dri ma ye nas zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:12267: yang ka dag pa'i lugs ma yin zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12268: 'di la dag rgyu'am dag rkyen nam /
NK104(phe)001:12269: dag pa log pa yod pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK104(phe)001:12270: ka zhes thog ma ka li rnams kyi sngon du
NK104(phe)001:12271: byung bas na ye nas dag pas bcos pa las
NK104(phe)001:12272: grol / rang dag pas 'bad pa las grol /
NK104(phe)001:12273: shugs kyis dag pas bsgrub bya las grol /
NK104(phe)001:12274: 'khrul ma myong bas ngo bo las grol /
NK104(phe)001:12275: 'khrul ba la mi gnas pas rang bzhin las grol /
NK104(phe)001:12276: 'khrul ba mi srid pas thugs rje las grol ba /
NK104(phe)001:12277: gal te 'khor ba'i chos ma dag go zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12279: ma 'khrul bya ba tsam du yang ma grub pas ma rig pa dang dag pas ming med /
NK104(phe)001:12280: snang ba dang mi snang ba ma grub pas yul gzung ba dang 'dzin pa rang dag pas /
NK104(phe)001:12281: nyon mongs pa'i gzhi stongs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12282: ma rig pa ma dag pas 'khrul te /
NK104(phe)001:12283: sems can gyi 'khrul gzhi sna tshogs su 'byung ba 'di zhes 'gegs zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12284: de la lan du ston pas gsungs pa sems dpa' chen po zhes bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:12285: ngo bo ka dag pa'i yon tan tsam du de
NK104(phe)001:12286: nyid kyi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir ro
NK104(phe)001:12287: // ma rig pa rang ka dag yin byas kyang lto ba med do //
NK104(phe)001:12288: ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i rtsal lam yon tan
NK104(phe)001:12289: de'am ma 'gags pa'i chos nyid kyi rol bar snang
NK104(phe)001:12290: ba'i phyir ro // de la brtsad pa /
NK104(phe)001:12291: sems dpa' nyid kyis yang gsol pa /
NK104(phe)001:12292: kye ston pa ngo bo ka dag gi rang bzhin nyid lhun grub yin pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12293: khams gsum gyi sems can 'di dag sangs rgyas su rang grol bar rigs te /
NK104(phe)001:12294: ye nas ngo bo la lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12295: dang po dam bca' ma grub la /
NK104(phe)001:12296: ngo bo ma yin pas rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12297: gnyis pa gtan tshigs ma grub ste ka dag gi
NK104(phe)001:12298: ngo bo la lhun grub ces grub mi srid la
NK104(phe)001:12299: / gsum pa gnod byed kyang grub pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12300: ngo bo ka nas dag pa lhun grub rgyu 'bras
NK104(phe)001:12301: 'brel so dang bcas pa nyid phan tshun 'gal lo
NK104(phe)001:12302: // de la ston pas lan du gsungs pa 'di ka dag la dri ma gang yang med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12303: dngos gzhi ngo bo ka dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:12304: sems can ma grol bas shes so zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12305: ma grol ba dang grol ba rnams kyang chos nyid kyi rtsal lam rol par snang ba ste /
NK104(phe)001:12306: ka dag rang gi ngo bo la grol bar grub pa med pas ngo bo zang thal /
NK104(phe)001:12307: ma grol bar kyang grub pa med pas rang bzhin la 'gag pa med /
NK104(phe)001:12308: grol ma grol gnyis snang las 'das pas thugs rje la ris dang phyogs med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12309: sdud pa pos ston pa la brtsad pa /
NK104(phe)001:12310: byang chub sems dpas yang gsol pa /
NK104(phe)001:12311: gzhi dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul gyi ngo bo nyid ni ka dag pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12312: rang bzhin la lhun gyis grub ces pa 'di la'ang dgos pa med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12313: ngo bo'i cha nas ka dag la /
NK104(phe)001:12314: rang bzhin la lhun gyis grub na ci lto ste khyab byed ma grub pas so //
NK104(phe)001:12315: 'o na ngo bo ka dag pa'i phyir /
NK104(phe)001:12317: yang na rang bzhin la lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK104(phe)001:12318: ngo bo ka nas dag pa zhes bya ba min par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12319: chos nyid la gang yang grub pa med kyang sems
NK104(phe)001:12320: can gyi snang tshul la ngo bo ka dag par
NK104(phe)001:12321: rang bzhin lhun grub na 'gegs pa'i rigs pa mi
NK104(phe)001:12322: rnyed do // ston pas lan du phyir brgal ba
NK104(phe)001:12323: ston pas gsungs pa dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul
NK104(phe)001:12324: rnyed do // / gang gis kyang brjod pa'i tshig tsam du grub pa med pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12325: brjod bya dang rjod byed kyi brjod pa sgra dang tshig rang bzhin bral bas na /
NK104(phe)001:12326: ngo bo ka dag bya ba gang du'ang grub pa med de /
NK104(phe)001:12327: lhun grub tu ga la srid do //
NK104(phe)001:12328: 'o na ka dag ces brjod pa'i sgra yis nyams so zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12329: brjod pa'i tshig dang tha snyad yin pas 'gal ba med do //
NK104(phe)001:12331: ngo bo ka dag la ci'i ngo bor kyang grub pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:12332: dngos po'i gshis la yi ge med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12333: tshig gis 'di la gnod pa dang bral lo //
NK104(phe)001:12335: gnod pa med pa'i gnad kyis phan pa tsam du'ang ma grub pas /
NK104(phe)001:12336: ngo bo ka dag ces bya ba'i 'dod pa nyams so zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12337: ka nas dag pas zhe 'dod khas len med do //
NK104(phe)001:12338: 'dod pa byung na chos nyid ma yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12339: khas blang rgyu gcig byung na gzhi ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12340: 'dod pa med na ka nas dag ces brjod pa nyams so zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12341: brjod pa'i tshig yin la ka dag tshig tu grub pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12342: tshig tsam du ka dag ces byung ngo zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12343: tshig ka dag ma yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12344: ka dag tshig ma yin pas so //
NK104(phe)001:12345: tshig ka dag ma yin na /
NK104(phe)001:12346: tshig gis ka dag gang gis 'gegs zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12347: tshig gzhi ma yin pas ka dag tshig tsam du grub mi srid do //
NK104(phe)001:12348: 'o na gal te khas len med na khas len
NK104(phe)001:12349: med cees brjod pa de ming med ces ming du
NK104(phe)001:12351: don gyis khas len pa yin no zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12352: brjod pa tsam gyis khas len du 'gro na /
NK104(phe)001:12353: khyod phung po gsum pa yin zhes brjod na /
NK104(phe)001:12354: phung po gsum pa yin nam ste /
NK104(phe)001:12355: ma yin pa bzhin du brjod pa tsam gyis khas len pa'i rgyu med do //
NK104(phe)001:12356: yang na skye bu nga thams cad mkhyen pa yin zhes brjod na /
NK104(phe)001:12357: de thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK104(phe)001:12358: de'i phyir na sems can 'khor 'das la bdag tu
NK104(phe)001:12359: 'dzin pa'i blo sna tshogs su 'gyu ba'i ngos nas
NK104(phe)001:12360: gcal na gzhi gnas lugs rim pa bdun ltar dmigs
NK104(phe)001:12361: pa'i yul la byung ba ste /
NK104(phe)001:12362: de ltar blo'i bye brag dran pa 'gyu byed sna tshogs su byung bas /
NK104(phe)001:12363: de la dgongs pa yin gyis /
NK104(phe)001:12364: yang dag par blo tha dad pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12365: tshig gi gnod pa srid kyang don gyi ngo bo la phan gnod dang bral te /
NK104(phe)001:12366: dper na nam mkha' la mtshon cha brgyab pa bzhin no //
NK104(phe)001:12367: skyes bus nam mkha' la mtshon cha rgyab pa rang yid khos pa las /
NK104(phe)001:12368: nam mkha' la phan btags pa dang gnod pa bskyal ba gang yang med pa bzhin du /
NK104(phe)001:12369: blo'i rnam par rtog pa dran pa dang bsam pa ma 'gags pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12370: tshig tu thal zhes brjod kyang rang yid khos pa las /
NK104(phe)001:12371: ngo bo la phan gnod gang du'ang grub pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12372: gal te tshig gis skyon de don la 'ong ngo zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12373: 'o na tshig gis rang gis dmigs pa skyes bu
NK104(phe)001:12374: gcig gi lus la mtshon cha'i char dbab par dmigs
NK104(phe)001:12375: nas / tshig tu yang skyes bu khyod kyi lus
NK104(phe)001:12376: la mtshon cha dbab bo zhes tshig tu brjod pas
NK104(phe)001:12377: nas / / don la yang char dbab par 'gyur ram ste mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK104(phe)001:12378: de yang tshig gi gnod pa phan pa ngo bo la khyad par med do //
NK104(phe)001:12379: yang sems can blo'i rtog pa la dgongs nas rdzogs
NK104(phe)001:12380: pa chen po 'dod pa rang shar ba'i ngos nas
NK104(phe)001:12381: rdzogs pa chen po ye ji bzhin par smra ba
NK104(phe)001:12382: 'khrul ma 'khrul med par 'dod pa'i lugs la phyir
NK104(phe)001:12383: brgal ba / 'khrul pa med na sems can gang
NK104(phe)001:12384: nas byung na ma 'khrul pa med na thams cad
NK104(phe)001:12385: mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'gegs sam zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12386: sems can shes bya la grub pa med pas 'khrul pa zhes grub ma myong ngo //
NK104(phe)001:12387: thams cad mkhyen pa zhes blo la grub pa med
NK104(phe)001:12388: pas ngo bo la btags pa mtha' dag gis stong
NK104(phe)001:12389: pa'o // yang rdzogs pa chen po thog ma bar
NK104(phe)001:12390: smra ba 'khrul ma myong bar 'dod pa'i lugs la
NK104(phe)001:12391: pa'o // phyir brgal ba / 'khrul ma myong ba de /
NK104(phe)001:12393: glo bur ba yin zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12394: ye nas 'khrul ma myong ba'i gnad kyis da lta yang 'khrul pa la mi gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12395: 'o na ye nas ma 'khrul pa de la 'khor 'das grub bam /
NK104(phe)001:12397: 'khor 'das gang du'ang ma grub pas 'khrul ma myong ngo //
NK104(phe)001:12398: 'o na da lta 'khrul pa la mi gnas pa'i phyir /
NK104(phe)001:12399: sems can rtog pa sna tshogs su 'khrul pa 'di 'gegs sam zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12400: sems can grub pa khyod kyis mthong ngam /
NK104(phe)001:12401: mthong na de la ltos pa'i sangs rgyas kyang mthong par 'gyur te /
NK104(phe)001:12402: yang mngon sum gyis bsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:12403: yang rdzogs pa chen po dong sprugs par smra ba
NK104(phe)001:12404: dang 'khrul mi srid par 'dod pa'i lugs la phyir
NK104(phe)001:12405: brgal ba / 'khrul mi srid na chad par smra ba dang khyad par med do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12406: chad pa ni snga phyi mi bden la da lta'i shes pa glo bur 'dod pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12407: 'di ni dang po 'khrul ma myong ba'i gnad kyis /
NK104(phe)001:12408: da lta'ang 'khrul pa la mi gnas te /
NK104(phe)001:12410: tha ma 'khrul mi srid pas khams gsum du mi brgyud pa'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:12411: yang rdzogs pa chen po 'khrul gzhi bar smra ba
NK104(phe)001:12412: yon tan dang skyon du 'dod pa'i lugs la phyir
NK104(phe)001:12413: brgal ba / yon tan du byung bas skyon ma byung la /
NK104(phe)001:12414: skyon du grub pas yon tan rdzogs mi srid do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12415: yon tan gyis ngos nas ka dag la /
NK104(phe)001:12416: skyon rtsal dang rol par snang na 'gag pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12417: rdzogs pa chen po gnyis snang du smra ba rtsal
NK104(phe)001:12418: dang yon tan du 'dod pa'i lugs la brgal ba
NK104(phe)001:12419: ni / rtsal du byung bas yon tan ma yin no zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12427: mi stong pa la sogs pa thams cad chos nyid
NK104(phe)001:12428: ka nas dag pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal yin pas
NK104(phe)001:12429: rang dag la / yon tan du shar bas rang rdzogs pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12430: thams cad yod med kyi rdzong la bros so //
NK104(phe)001:12431: yang rdzogs pa chen po skyon med rang grol du
NK104(phe)001:12432: smra ba dri med ye dag tu 'dod pa'i lugs
NK104(phe)001:12433: la / brtsad pa dri ma ye nas dag pas
NK104(phe)001:12434: sems can gyi blo'i rtog pa mi rigs so zhe
NK104(phe)001:12435: la / na / dri ma ye nas dag pas 'gro ba 'di kun ngas ma mthong /
NK104(phe)001:12437: 'di ni rdzogs pa chen po chos nyid par smra
NK104(phe)001:12438: ba ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rjer 'dod pa'i lugs
NK104(phe)001:12439: la brtsad pa / ngo bor snang bas rang bzhin ma yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12440: thugs rje'ang ma yin no zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12441: ngo bo la blo dang bral bas rang bzhin rang shar du ma 'gags /
NK104(phe)001:12442: thugs rje la byung lugs su rdzogs pas skyon las 'das pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12443: yang rdzogs pa chen po khas mi len du smra ba gang yang med pa'i lugs la ni /
NK104(phe)001:12444: snang stong la sogs pa gang du yang khas mi len na /
NK104(phe)001:12445: ming med ming du song ba dang 'dra'o //
NK104(phe)001:12446: phyogs gcig min na gang yang med pa'i 'dod pa nyams so zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12449: yod dang med pa 'di ni med pa'i chos yin te zhes pas so //
NK104(phe)001:12450: dngos po 'dug tshul la ci'i ngo bor kyang grub pa med pas so //
NK104(phe)001:12451: yang rdzogs pa chen po rgyun chad du smra ba
NK104(phe)001:12452: ltar snang sems tsam du 'dod pa'i lugs la ni
NK104(phe)001:12453: / ngo bo la ye shes rgyun chad pas ltar snang sems tsam du 'dod pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12454: ltar snang sems su snang ba'i phyir ye shes rgyun ma chad do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12455: shes bya dang shes byed du med pas ye shes
NK104(phe)001:12456: tsam du dngos po la grub pa med pas na
NK104(phe)001:12457: / ltar snang la sems tsam du snang ba ma 'gags pa ci lto //
NK104(phe)001:12458: sems ni ye shes dngos ma yin pas so //
NK104(phe)001:12459: de yang ngo bo ka dag la ye shes snang na ni spros par 'gyur la /
NK104(phe)001:12460: de'i phyir na ye shes rang gi ngos nas ni med la /
NK104(phe)001:12461: ye shes kyi ldog pas na mkhyen pa'i cha rdzogs
NK104(phe)001:12462: pa'i ngos nas snang du rung ba la ma dmigs
NK104(phe)001:12463: pa'o // ye shes de snang na dngos po'i gnas
NK104(phe)001:12464: lugs ye shes dang bcas pa de yul dang yul
NK104(phe)001:12466: de ltar na ye shes rang gi ngos nas rgyun chad de /
NK104(phe)001:12467: de'ang ye nas chad pa yin pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12468: phyi rol pa'i 'dod pa lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12469: de'ang dper na rgyu bud shing zad pas me rgyun chad de mi snang ba dang 'dra'o //
NK104(phe)001:12470: gal te snang bar 'dod ni gnod pa'i rigs pa 'ong ngo //
NK104(phe)001:12471: yang rdzogs pa chen po gnyis 'dzin du smra ba
NK104(phe)001:12472: 'khrul snang glo bur du 'dod pa'i lugs ni grub
NK104(phe)001:12475: 'dod pa tshig tsam du bkod pa de rten dang
NK104(phe)001:12476: brten pa'i tshul yin pas na don dam pa spros
NK104(phe)001:12478: kun rdzob tha snyad du snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:12479: zhes de dag gis ni bsdus pa'i don gnyis pa
NK104(phe)001:12480: gnas lugs chen po bzhir 'dod rang shar bas bstan
NK104(phe)001:12481: pa la nang don dgur byas nas bstan no //
NK104(phe)001:12482: da ni bsdus pa'i don gsum pa dri med rdzogs
NK104(phe)001:12483: pa chen po la rang 'dod tshig gis gtan la
NK104(phe)001:12485: nang don drug gis bstan pa'i dang po rdzogs pa
NK104(phe)001:12486: chen po bya ba dang bral ba ka nas dag
NK104(phe)001:12488: ye shes mngon sum du snang yang mtshan ma las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12489: de nas nyi ma 'dus pa'i zhes pa la sogs pa bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:12490: bka' stsal pa yan chod gzhung gsal /
NK104(phe)001:12491: kye ma zhes nges pa bos te /
NK104(phe)001:12492: nyi ma 'dus pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po zhes bos nas /
NK104(phe)001:12493: ka dag gi gnas lugs gong du ma shes na
NK104(phe)001:12494: 'di zur nyid ni yang zur cig ces gdams te
NK104(phe)001:12495: / 'og nas ston pa'i ye shes nyid ni rnam gsum gyis /
NK104(phe)001:12496: ka nas dag pa'i gzhi'i khyad par tshig tu bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12497: 'di ni gzhi la ye shes yongs pa'i lugs te /
NK104(phe)001:12498: ye shes de yang snang byed du med la /
NK104(phe)001:12499: mkhyen pa ma 'gags pa'i cha nas bzhag pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12500: gal te med na b+hud+d+ha'i mkhyen pa'i cha stongs pas na phyam chad pa'i skyon du 'gyur pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12501: de yang ye shes de gnas pa yin la snang bar ni mi 'dod do //
NK104(phe)001:12502: gnas pa'i phyir mkhyen pa rang sa na gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:12503: mi snang bas stong pa ngo bo nges gzung du yod pa ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12504: de yang gang la mi snang na gdul bya las ma dag pa la mi snang /
NK104(phe)001:12505: 'o na las dag pa la snang ngam zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12506: las dag pa la gnas pa'i cha tsam du ni snang du btub la /
NK104(phe)001:12507: mtshan nyid rang rgyud par ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12508: gang gi phyir mi snang na /
NK104(phe)001:12509: mtshan nyid rang rgyud pa ma yin pa'i phyir mi snang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:12510: gang mi snang na ye shes de gzung cha dang 'dzin char ni snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12511: de yang tha snyad btags pa'i dbang gis na /
NK104(phe)001:12512: ngo bo'i ye shes stong la /
NK104(phe)001:12514: thugs rje rig par gnas pa tsam la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK104(phe)001:12515: stong pa phyam chad pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12516: gsal ba ris can du ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12517: shes rig blo'i spyod pas ni ma yin pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12518: stong pa'i ngos nas ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes kyis /
NK104(phe)001:12519: ma rig pa la sogs pa'i 'khrul pa dri ma 'du byed pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12521: mig dang gzugs la sogs pa'i bcu gnyis dang bral bas na /
NK104(phe)001:12522: ngo bo de nyid ye shes 'khrul ma myong bar bzhugs pas na //
NK104(phe)001:12523: 'khrul pa gtan 'bebs kyi rtsis las 'das pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12524: de yang gsal ba'i ngos nas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub kyi ye shes kyis /
NK104(phe)001:12525: 'di ni ma rig pa las 'khrul pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12526: 'du byed las 'khrul pa zhes pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12527: rnam par shes pa las 'khrul zhes bya ba la
NK104(phe)001:12528: sogs pa'i 'khrul pa'i tshes gis rang bzhin la lhun
NK104(phe)001:12529: gyis grub pa la gnod pa dang bral ba'i phyir
NK104(phe)001:12530: na phan pa dang grub pa med do //
NK104(phe)001:12531: de yang rig pa 'char tshul ma 'gags pa'i ngos nas thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes kyis /
NK104(phe)001:12532: ye shes gsum tha dad pa ma yin te /
NK104(phe)001:12533: stong gsal rig pa'i snying po can du thams cad
NK104(phe)001:12534: chos kyi dbyings gcig pu 'brel bar snang bas na
NK104(phe)001:12535: / chos nyid ka dag pa rang gi ngo gang la dbyer med cing gnyis su med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12536: de lta bu'i ye shes gsum dang 'du 'bral med
NK104(phe)001:12537: par gnas pa'i gnas lugs de re zhig tshig gis
NK104(phe)001:12538: mtshon pa tsam du gtan la phab na /
NK104(phe)001:12541: blo'i 'khrul pa med pa'i tshe na /
NK104(phe)001:12542: ye shes gsum po yang gnas pa la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK104(phe)001:12543: snang bar med pas na de ltar na ngo bo nyid ka dag la /
NK104(phe)001:12544: ye shes rang gi ngo bo nas yang dag par
NK104(phe)001:12545: ye shes med cing de la brten pa'i sku yang
NK104(phe)001:12546: lus kyi mtha' zad pa'i phyir med do //
NK104(phe)001:12547: de'i phyir na ye shes dang sku las byung ba'i
NK104(phe)001:12548: 'od lnga yang med pas de la kha dog lngar
NK104(phe)001:12550: kha dog nyer lnga 'dzin pa'i cha yang med la /
NK104(phe)001:12551: kha dog nyer lnga 'dzin pa rnams dang ye nas bral byas gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12552: 'o na stong par yod dam zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12553: stong pa tsam du 'dzin dang stong pa ngo bo
NK104(phe)001:12554: gang gi ngo bor kyang grub pa med pas na
NK104(phe)001:12555: / rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12557: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa dang de las
NK104(phe)001:12558: byung ba'i 'khrul pa rnams drug rtsa ba'i nyon mongs
NK104(phe)001:12559: pa dang / nyi shu nye ba'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12560: lnga kun tu 'gro ba la sogs pa sems dang
NK104(phe)001:12561: sems las byung ba'i nyon mongs kyi ngo bo dang
NK104(phe)001:12562: / dbye ba'i rnam pa ye nas mi srid pas /
NK104(phe)001:12563: ka dag la smos ci dgos te yod pa min no //
NK104(phe)001:12564: 'o na de rnams gang du song zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12565: yon tan 'char tshul gyi cha nas gzhal na ka dag gi rang bzhin nyid kyi snang ba las /
NK104(phe)001:12566: snang cha'am de la mtshan mar 'dzin pa ye med de /
NK104(phe)001:12567: ye shes de'ang snang cha med la gzhi gnas su yod pas snang ba la 'char du ni med /
NK104(phe)001:12568: gnas pa'i cha nas ye shes lnga'i cha kha dog lnga rang snang du 'dzin pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12569: gnas shing yod pa tsam la rang gsal bas na ye shes yod ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12570: ye shes gsum po de yang gang zag gi rgyud
NK104(phe)001:12571: la sbyar na stong gsal rig pa'i snying por gnas
NK104(phe)001:12572: pas na / shes shing rig pa'i cha rnams tshang gzhi la gnas pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12573: sems can gyi dus na'ang gnas pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12574: de'i don rtogs na sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12575: ka nas dag pas yul 'di yin la dmigs pa med pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12577: de la ma gnas pas phyi gzung ba'i yul rtog
NK104(phe)001:12578: dpyod dang bcas pa gang yang med pa'i phyir ro
NK104(phe)001:12579: // de ltar gnas pas de la nang dang phyi
NK104(phe)001:12580: rol gnyis ka na rnam par rtog pa'i 'dzin cha
NK104(phe)001:12581: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa phra ba tsam yang med
NK104(phe)001:12582: // pas / yul kha dog yul can ye shes
NK104(phe)001:12583: med par 'od las 'das pa'i chos nyid kyi ye
NK104(phe)001:12584: gdangs su gzhi la gnas pa'i cha ma 'gags pas
NK104(phe)001:12585: // pas / / gzhi la babs kyis grub pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12586: de yang glo bur ba'am dum bu lta bu ma
NK104(phe)001:12587: yin par ye thog ma nyid nas ni gzhi la
NK104(phe)001:12589: de nyid lus kyi rdzogs pa'i phyir na sku las
NK104(phe)001:12590: 'das pa'i rang mdangs su gang yang ma phye mi
NK104(phe)001:12591: 'dzin pas so // yul dang shes pa'i rnam pa
NK104(phe)001:12592: gnyis ka dag pa'i phyag rgya chen po ra gnas
NK104(phe)001:12593: 'dzin pas so // pa ni / gang zag gi dus na phyag gzung bya /
NK104(phe)001:12594: rgya gdab bya chen po de dang mi 'bral bar gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12595: de yang gang zag la snang ba'i ngos nas 'on
NK104(phe)001:12596: te gzhi ka dag ni rang bzhin gyi snang ba
NK104(phe)001:12597: la / rnam par dkar dmar gyi shes pa mtshan
NK104(phe)001:12598: ma can du dmigs par snang ba ye nas med
NK104(phe)001:12599: la / de / rang snang du snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12600: de yang ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i ye shes kyi don gyi cha la 'di ltar gnas te /
NK104(phe)001:12601: 'di dag ni yon tan gyi cha la snang ba ste /
NK104(phe)001:12602: de'ang dri ma dag pa'i ngos nas chos nyid kyi rang gdangs bskyed pa'i dkar po'i char /
NK104(phe)001:12603: shes bya la babs kyis gting gsal chen po nyid du gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12604: de ltar chos nyid gting gsal ngo bo'i bkrag bskyed pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12605: yon tan gyi 'char byed kyi ngos nas /
NK104(phe)001:12606: phyi rol gyi snang ba rang zad pa'i ser po'i cha /
NK104(phe)001:12607: mtshan ma snang ba la mi mngon gting nas phyi dang nang du med par rang ngo gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:12608: de ltar chos nyid rang gi ngo de la chags
NK104(phe)001:12609: med mdangs skyed pa rigs pa rang gis bcings pa
NK104(phe)001:12611: zhen pa rang dag pa'i gos nas chags pa rang zad dmar po'i char gnas te /
NK104(phe)001:12612: phyi rol yul la snang byed dam 'char byed du
NK104(phe)001:12613: med pa ni ye shes kyi gting gdangs gang dang
NK104(phe)001:12614: yang ma 'dres pa chen por gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12615: de ltar chos nyid rang sa nas ma 'dres so
NK104(phe)001:12616: so'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa ni kha dog dkar dmar
NK104(phe)001:12618: bya brtsal dang rlung la sogs pa'i bskyod pa rang bral ba'i phyir /
NK104(phe)001:12619: gzhi ka nas dag pa'i ngos nas rang bzhin du mdzad pa med pa'i ljang khur ni /
NK104(phe)001:12620: gzhi thog ma rnams kyi zer du yang dag par gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12621: de yang snang yul zhen yul gnyis kar med de /
NK104(phe)001:12622: babs kyis grub pa tsam las /
NK104(phe)001:12623: dbang po gzugs can la sogs par mi mngon gting nas gsal ba'i cha tshang bar gnas pa /
NK104(phe)001:12624: de'ang ye shes rang gi ngo bo gting gsal khyab pa'i 'brel byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12625: de la ngo bo rang dag pa'i ngos nas 'gyur med gting nas rdzogs pa'i mthing khar ni /
NK104(phe)001:12626: de'ang dkar dmar ris can gyi yul med par gzhi la ye rdzogs byas pa med par gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12627: zhes dang po rdzogs pa chen po bya ba dang
NK104(phe)001:12628: bral ba ka nas dag pa rang gi gnas lugs
NK104(phe)001:12629: ye shes gsum du snang ba mtshan ma las 'das
NK104(phe)001:12630: pa bstan nas / da ni gnyis pa rdzogs pa
NK104(phe)001:12631: chen po ka dag gzhi snang gi khyad par las
NK104(phe)001:12632: ye shes rang gi ngo bo ji ltar gnas tshul
NK104(phe)001:12633: dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12634: de ltar de'i rang bzhin las /
NK104(phe)001:12635: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:12636: de ltar ni gong ma'i ye shes gsum po de chos kyi sku'i mkhyen pa'i cha yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12637: de'i ni chos sku de mi 'gyur ba'i cha nas
NK104(phe)001:12638: ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes su gnas pas
NK104(phe)001:12640: chos sku de la mkhyen pa'i go ma 'gags par
NK104(phe)001:12641: nang gsal du yod pas rang bzhin lhun grub kyi
NK104(phe)001:12642: ye shes su gnas pas rang gsal ma ltos pa'o
NK104(phe)001:12643: // chos sku'i mkhyen pa de yang phyogs med du
NK104(phe)001:12644: 'char bas thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes su
NK104(phe)001:12645: // gnas pas / gzhi de 'khor 'das gang gi yang phyogs su ma lhung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12646: rang bzhin la ye shes gsum rdzogs pa'i chos sku
NK104(phe)001:12647: ni mtshan ma ris can du yod pa lta bu
NK104(phe)001:12649: sku lus kyi 'brel ba dang bcas pa rang zad de /
NK104(phe)001:12650: sku rang gi ngos nas ni 'byed pa dang snang bar med la /
NK104(phe)001:12651: sku'i ldog pa nas ni snang la snang ba de
NK104(phe)001:12652: yang zhen yul snang ba'i mtshan nyid dang bral bar
NK104(phe)001:12653: snang ngo // snang ba tsam po de yang bcos pa'am glo bur ba ma yin te //
NK104(phe)001:12654: ye thog ma nas rang dag chen por gnas pa la /
NK104(phe)001:12655: 'byung pa'i mtha' rdzogs pas gsal ba ris med kyi 'od kyi rtse mor gnas /
NK104(phe)001:12656: lus kyi mtha' sku gsum 'du 'bral med /
NK104(phe)001:12657: chos can dang chos nyid kyi mtha' rdzogs pas chos nyid ka dag pa'i sa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12658: shes rab dang sems kyi mtha' rdzogs pas mkhyen pa
NK104(phe)001:12659: rang dag pa rnams kyi rtse mor gnas pas gzhi
NK104(phe)001:12660: rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12661: sku de yang snang byed dang bcas pa'i kha mig
NK104(phe)001:12662: dang phyag dang zhal du ni mi snang bas 'di
NK104(phe)001:12663: la dbang po lngar snang ba med do //
NK104(phe)001:12664: de yang lta byed du med pas dngos po'i rdos pa lus dang sems bcas pa med la /
NK104(phe)001:12665: mtshan ma ris can gyi kha dog rnams kyang rang dag pa'i phyir na /
NK104(phe)001:12666: shes bya rang gi mtshan nyid la babs kyis grub
NK104(phe)001:12667: pa las chos nyid gting gsal chen po'i gzhi mar
NK104(phe)001:12668: gnas so // de yang gang zag gi dus na
NK104(phe)001:12669: khyab bya rig pa khyab pa rig pa nyid kyi
NK104(phe)001:12670: dbyings stong pa la khyab pas dbyings rig 'du 'bral
NK104(phe)001:12671: gnas so // med pa'o // 'o na stong pa
NK104(phe)001:12672: nyi tshe ba lta bu ma yin nam zhe na
NK104(phe)001:12673: gnas so // med pa'o // / phyang nas chad pa'i stong pa bar can dang /
NK104(phe)001:12674: bems po'i stong pa 'gro 'ong med pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12675: snang ba'i stong pa rgyan nam mkha' lta bu ma yin par /
NK104(phe)001:12676: mkhyen pa ye shes kyi 'char byed ma 'gags pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12677: ngos nas gsal byed ye shes su snang ba'i cha
NK104(phe)001:12678: tshang bar rang ngo la ma 'gags pas /
NK104(phe)001:12679: gong ma'i sku de dag shes bya gnas tshul du dag pas snying po /
NK104(phe)001:12681: sems kyi snying po ye shes /
NK104(phe)001:12682: kha dog gi snying po rang gdangs /
NK104(phe)001:12683: thams cad bcud ka dag chen po'i gnas lugs su 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK104(phe)001:12684: de lta bu'i chos nyid de ma rig pa 'khrul pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12685: nyon mongs pa'i dri ma bdag gzhan dang /
NK104(phe)001:12686: rnam par rtog pa'i dri ma gzung 'dzin dang /
NK104(phe)001:12687: 'gyu ba phra rags kyi dri ma lus dang /
NK104(phe)001:12688: lta ba phyin ci log gi dri ma med cing
NK104(phe)001:12689: de dag rnams rang sar dag pas na ka dag
NK104(phe)001:12690: ces bya'o // de ltar gnas pa'i gzhi de la 'bad rtsol rnams rang bzhin gyis sangs //
NK104(phe)001:12691: ma rig pa la sogs pa rnams ye nas sangs pas ka dag ces bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12692: de'i mkhyen pa'i cha ma 'gags par rgyas pas ye shes tsam du ni bzhugs la /
NK104(phe)001:12693: snang byed par ni med pa rnams kyi gsang chen du gnas pa ni ngo bo yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12694: de'i rang bzhin gyi ni cha la babs kyis grub
NK104(phe)001:12695: pa las mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas par bzhugs so
NK104(phe)001:12696: // gzhi de'i thugs rje snang cha gdul bya'i ngo
NK104(phe)001:12697: gang la sna tshogs pa las chos nyid stong pa
NK104(phe)001:12698: kun 'byung gi tshul du snang cha 'gag pa med
NK104(phe)001:12699: // pa las / longs sku mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12700: ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa ni gzhan
NK104(phe)001:12701: // pa las / na bstan no // de ltar
NK104(phe)001:12702: gzhi de'i thugs rje'i cha nas sprul pa'i sku la
NK104(phe)001:12703: shes bya ji ltar ba'i ye shes kyi dngos po'i
NK104(phe)001:12704: gnas lugs nyid ka mkhyen la /
NK104(phe)001:12705: shes bya ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes gdul
NK104(phe)001:12706: bya'i bsam pa mkhyen pa rnam pa gnyis su mi
NK104(phe)001:12707: gnas na / stong pa nam mkha' dang khyad par mi rnyed do //
NK104(phe)001:12708: gal te ye shes rgyun chad do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12709: gzugs sku gnyis kyis sems can gyi don byed dam mi byed /
NK104(phe)001:12710: mi byed na b+hud+d+ha pa la god med la /
NK104(phe)001:12711: byed na ye shes rgyun chad pa nyams so //
NK104(phe)001:12712: byed kyang ye shes med do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12713: lo ka ba'i shes pa dang khyad med do //
NK104(phe)001:12714: sprul sku'i ye shes gnyis po de gzhi la med
NK104(phe)001:12715: na sprul sku sangs rgyas ma yin pa'i skyon du
NK104(phe)001:12716: 'gro bas na / ye shes des don byed dam mi byed /
NK104(phe)001:12717: mi byed na rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12719: dngos su byed dam brgyud nas byed ce na /
NK104(phe)001:12720: ye shes de gnas pa'i cha nas bzhag pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12721: dngos po rang rgyud pa lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12722: 'o na dbu ma ye shes snang bar 'dod pa dang khyad par mi rnyed do ce na /
NK104(phe)001:12723: dbu ma na rigs pa'i shes pa dang bcas te snang bar 'dod pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12724: 'di ni ye shes rang gi ngos nas ni mi snang la /
NK104(phe)001:12725: ye shes kyi ldog pa nas snang zhes tshig gis
NK104(phe)001:12726: gtan la dbab tu btub pas na ye shes yod
NK104(phe)001:12728: ye shes de yang dngos dang brgyud pa zhes dngos po la grub pa med pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12729: ye shes kyi ldog pa nas snang ba'i cha la rnam par gnas pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12730: stong pa nyid kyi ngos nas ye shes med ces
NK104(phe)001:12731: bya ba tsam la sgro 'dogs pa'i snang ba rang
NK104(phe)001:12732: dag pa las / de'ang med ces mtha' bkag pa la dgongs pa yin la /
NK104(phe)001:12733: yang dag par ltos pa'i ngos nas ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12734: de'ang dper na nyi ma yod pas nyi ma'i 'od
NK104(phe)001:12735: dgag tu ma btub par shugs las 'byung ba dang
NK104(phe)001:12736: 'dra bar / gzhi ka nas dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK104(phe)001:12737: shugs gyis ni gdul bya las dag pa rnams la
NK104(phe)001:12739: de'ang snang byed dang snang cha rang gi rtsol ba med par /
NK104(phe)001:12740: de yang dngos su mdzad pa'i rtsol ba ye nas med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12741: ye nas rtsol ba med par sus kyang ma byas
NK104(phe)001:12742: par snang ba'i tshul dag tu sku rnam pa gsum
NK104(phe)001:12743: dbyer med par ye nas ye shes dang shes bya
NK104(phe)001:12744: rang gi mtshan nyid la 'byed pa med par snang
NK104(phe)001:12745: ste / snang ba de yang ris can stong pa gzung yul dang bcas pa ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12746: de'ang dper na nyi ma las ni 'od bzhin du /
NK104(phe)001:12747: nyi ma nyid la 'od de la 'od snang bar
NK104(phe)001:12748: bya ba dang mi snang bar bya ba gnyis med
NK104(phe)001:12749: do // de bzhin du ye shes de'ang rang shugs
NK104(phe)001:12750: las byung ba yin gyi chos nyid ka dag pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12751: ngo bo rang gis byas pa ma yin te /
NK104(phe)001:12752: chos nyid rang gi rang bzhin ye nas de ltar snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12753: gal te shes bya ji lta ba mkhyen pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12754: ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis med na /
NK104(phe)001:12755: dngos po gnas lugs bems po sa chu me rlung rnams dang khyad ci yod de /
NK104(phe)001:12756: 'di la shes pa'i cha gsal byed tsam du yod pa nyams su myong ba ni med do //
NK104(phe)001:12757: de'ang gsal byed du med na bems por 'gro la /
NK104(phe)001:12758: nyams su myong bar yod na sems tsam rnams dang khyad par med do //
NK104(phe)001:12759: gal te bems po lta bu ni ma yin la stong ngo zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12760: yang na stong pa phyam chad du 'di nyid 'gyur ba kho na'o //
NK104(phe)001:12761: de'i phyir na ye shes rgyun ma chad de /
NK104(phe)001:12762: ye shes kyi ldog pa nas snang ngo tsam du dngos po'i gnas lugs rang gi ngos nas shes /
NK104(phe)001:12763: rang don du dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs las dus gsum du mi g.yo bar shes la /
NK104(phe)001:12764: de nyid bya ba gang la'ang dngos su byed pa dang brgyud par byed pa med pas /
NK104(phe)001:12765: ka nas dag pa'i don ji ltar gnas pa de bzhin du mkhyen pa'i phyir ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12766: de'ang ye shes rang gi ngo bo'i cha nas ni mkhyen pa tsam du med la /
NK104(phe)001:12767: thugs rje'i gzugs sku gnyis po'i cha'i ye shes kyis
NK104(phe)001:12768: gzhi shes pa'i rang gi ngo bor gnas pa de
NK104(phe)001:12769: nyid kyis dngos po'i gnas lugs nang gsal du mkhyen
NK104(phe)001:12772: gal te shes bya ji ltar ba mkhyen pa'i cha
NK104(phe)001:12773: med na phyi rol mu stegs pa rigs pa can
NK104(phe)001:12774: du smra ba 'byung ba bzhi don dam par 'dod
NK104(phe)001:12775: pa ste / sa la sems yod pas rtsi shing la sogs pa skyed par nus pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12776: me la yod pas 'bar zhing bud shing sreg cing mched par nus pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12777: chu la yod pas gcig tu mi gnas shing 'gro bar nus pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12778: rlung la yod pas 'byed cing skyod pa'i las sna
NK104(phe)001:12779: tshogs byed ces pa'i gzugs 'dzin pa dang khyad par
NK104(phe)001:12781: yang gdul bya'i ngos nas shes pa gdul bya rnams kyi bsam pa mkhyen la /
NK104(phe)001:12782: lo ka rang rgyud pa'i bya ba byed pa gdul bya'i yul ji snyed pa mkhyen pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12783: chos kyi sku ci'i ngo bor kyang ma grub pa la /
NK104(phe)001:12784: dper na nyi ma la 'od rang bzhin gyis byung ba ltar /
NK104(phe)001:12785: gzugs sku gnyis kyis gdul bya'i 'gro ba rnams yang dag pa la 'god par byed pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12786: shugs las byung ba las dngos po rang rgyud ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12787: de'ang ka dag gi gzhi'i thugs rje'i ye shes kyis
NK104(phe)001:12788: 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i don byed pa'i ngos nas
NK104(phe)001:12789: gdul bya las dag pa dang ma dag pa rnams
NK104(phe)001:12790: kyi bsams pa mkhyen pas don du 'gyur ba dang
NK104(phe)001:12791: mi 'gyur ba'i bya ba shes pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12792: shes bya ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'di
NK104(phe)001:12793: med na stong pa phyam chad pa'i skyon du 'gyur
NK104(phe)001:12794: bas na / dper na nam mkha' nyid dang mtshungs te /
NK104(phe)001:12795: don byed nus pa mtha' dag gis stong pa'i phyir ro /
NK104(phe)001:12796: 'o na gdul bya dang gnas lugs kyi ye shes
NK104(phe)001:12797: su 'byung ba gsum sogs pa'am yang na gcig tu
NK104(phe)001:12799: 'di ni yul la dgongs pa yin la dngos po'i
NK104(phe)001:12800: gnas lugs las ma g.yos pa'i cha nas ci lta
NK104(phe)001:12801: bar bzhag la / don byed ma 'gags pa'i cha nas ji snyed par bzhag pa yin gyis /
NK104(phe)001:12802: gnyis po de grangs nges pa'am dus nges pa ni ma yin no //
NK104(phe)001:12803: 'o na gnyis su smos pa la dgos pa med do zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12804: de ni gong ltar yul la dgongs pa yin pa
NK104(phe)001:12805: las ma gtogs pa gnyis su nges pa med pa
NK104(phe)001:12807: gal te gnyis su byung yang chos nyid dam ye
NK104(phe)001:12808: shes rang gi ngo bo tha dad pa lta bu
NK104(phe)001:12810: zhes gnyis pa rdzogs pa chen po ka dag gzhi
NK104(phe)001:12811: snang rang gi khyad par las ye shes rang gi
NK104(phe)001:12812: ngo bo ji ltar gnas tshul dang bcas pa bstan
NK104(phe)001:12813: nas // da ni gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po
NK104(phe)001:12814: ka dag rang gnas chen po'i ngang las thugs rje
NK104(phe)001:12815: rtsal gyi 'char lugs bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12816: de phyir thams cad mkhyen pas zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:12817: de'i phyir na snang ba thams cad mkhyen pas sprul pa'i skus yul dang yul dag pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12818: ma dag pa rnams mkhyen pas snod bcud kyis bsdus
NK104(phe)001:12819: pa ji snyed pa skyu ru ra rlon pa lag
NK104(phe)001:12820: mthil du bzhag pa bzhin du mkhyen pas /
NK104(phe)001:12821: gdul bya rnams kyi bsam pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
NK104(phe)001:12822: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye
NK104(phe)001:12823: shes thugs rje'i cha la snang bas gsung rang byung
NK104(phe)001:12824: gi yi ge drug las rang sgra byung ba ljags
NK104(phe)001:12825: kyi dbang po la 'phros pas gdul bya ji snyed
NK104(phe)001:12827: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnams dus gcig la mkhyen
NK104(phe)001:12828: pa'i rang ngo la phyi nang med par zang thal
NK104(phe)001:12829: bar mkhyen pa / 'di kun sems can gyi dran
NK104(phe)001:12830: pa rang rgyud pa bdag dang bcas pas bzung ba
NK104(phe)001:12831: bar mkhyen pa / med de / thugs rje rtsal
NK104(phe)001:12832: gyi 'char lugs ma 'gags pa las rang bzhin nyid
NK104(phe)001:12834: phyi yul la bzung bas bdag dang nang sems can
NK104(phe)001:12835: la 'dzin pas gzhan dang phyi nang kun gyi yul
NK104(phe)001:12836: la rags par mi gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:12837: de'ang chos nyid la babs kyis grub pas na chos
NK104(phe)001:12838: nyid gting gsal bag la nyal rab tu phra ba'i
NK104(phe)001:12839: char snang ba'o // gang zag gi dus na gong
NK104(phe)001:12840: ma'i rtsal las ye shes kyi 'char byed las 'od
NK104(phe)001:12841: lnga'i 'char byed du gnas pas na ye shes lnga'i
NK104(phe)001:12842: char snang ba'o // rtsal / 'di ni sems can
NK104(phe)001:12843: rnams kyi lam ye shes su 'char bar byed pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12844: gzhi chos nyid nyams kyi snang ba gong du 'phel
NK104(phe)001:12845: bar byed pa'i sa bon las myu gu de las
NK104(phe)001:12846: ldong bu dang 'dab ma dang me tog dang 'bras
NK104(phe)001:12847: bu bzhin du 'phel bar byed pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12848: ye shes las byung ba'i 'od de'i kha dog dang /
NK104(phe)001:12849: dbyibs su lam la snang ba 'di'i snang ba ma 'gags par shar pa na /
NK104(phe)001:12850: gang ma'i thugs rje'i cha las sprul pa'i sku'i don byed pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12852: dper na nad rang dang mthun pa'i sman gyi nus pas so so'i nad 'joms pa bzhin du /
NK104(phe)001:12853: sprul pa'i skus 'gro ba rigs drug rnams la rang
NK104(phe)001:12854: dang mthun pa'i gzugs thub pa drug ltar sprul nas
NK104(phe)001:12855: 'gro ba gang la gang 'dul dang mthun par snang
NK104(phe)001:12856: la / rnal 'byor bas ye shes lnga'i kha dog
NK104(phe)001:12857: dang dbyibs kyi snang ba la brten nas bla ma'i
NK104(phe)001:12858: man ngag dang mthun par snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12859: de'i phyir na sku gsum rims kyis rnal 'byor pa'i
NK104(phe)001:12860: lam la thugs rje rtsal gyi 'char lugs su byung
NK104(phe)001:12861: ba'o / zhes gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po ka
NK104(phe)001:12862: dag rang gnas chen po'i ngang las thugs rje rtsal
NK104(phe)001:12864: da ni bzhi ba rdzogs pa chen po ka dag rang gnas chen po'i gzhi las ngo bo /
NK104(phe)001:12866: thugs rje gsum gyi 'char tshul bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12867: de phyir rang gshis 'dug tshul las /
NK104(phe)001:12869: gtan tshigs ngo bo ka dag pa de'i phyir na
NK104(phe)001:12870: rang gi shes bya'i gshis dngos po gnas lugs kyi
NK104(phe)001:12871: / 'dug tshul las de nyid mi 'gyur ba'i cha nas ngo bo dang /
NK104(phe)001:12872: de nyid gsal ba'i cha nas rang bzhin dang /
NK104(phe)001:12873: de nyid kyi 'char tshul ma 'gags pa'i cha nas thugs rje'i ni snang bar /
NK104(phe)001:12874: yang dag par dmigs pa yul gyi blo can rnams la snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12875: de yang ngo bo gang du ma grub pas chos kyi sku zhes byas kyang 'gal ba med la /
NK104(phe)001:12876: de'i rang bzhin snang cha gsal bar snang bas longs
NK104(phe)001:12877: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes byas kyang 'gal ba med
NK104(phe)001:12878: do // de'i thugs rje'i cha la sprul pa'i skus rang don du dngos po'i gnas lugs mkhyen pas /
NK104(phe)001:12879: shes bya ji lta ba bzhin du mkhyen la /
NK104(phe)001:12880: gzhan don du gdul bya'i bsam pa mkhyen pas /
NK104(phe)001:12881: shes bya'i chos ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK104(phe)001:12882: gnyis su snang bas na sprul pa'i skur btags kyang
NK104(phe)001:12884: de yang 'bad dang brtsal ba bya ba dang byed pa med par shar ba /
NK104(phe)001:12885: 'bad pa med pa'i spyad pas kyang 'gal ba med /
NK104(phe)001:12886: de ltar shar ba'i snang ba gang zag yang dag pa'i blo can dang /
NK104(phe)001:12887: phyin ci log gi blo rim gnyis kyi phyir na /
NK104(phe)001:12888: gdul bya las dag pa rnams la sprul pa'i sku'i
NK104(phe)001:12889: skabs nas shes bya ji lta ba mkhyen pas gzigs
NK104(phe)001:12890: la / phyin ci log gi blo can dang /
NK104(phe)001:12891: phyin ci log gi blo can rnams shes bya ji snyed pa mkhyen pas gzigs pas na /
NK104(phe)001:12892: ye shes kyi mdzad pa gnyis lta bu sems can la snang ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:12893: de yang rang bzhin ye nas rtsol sgrub rnams dang
NK104(phe)001:12894: bral bar snang bas 'bad pa med pa'i sgom par
NK104(phe)001:12896: de ltar na thugs rje'i rtsal la sangs rgyas rnams
NK104(phe)001:12897: kyi ye shes ni ka dag pa la babs kyis
NK104(phe)001:12898: grub pas na / ngo bo skur gtan la phab kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK104(phe)001:12899: rang bzhin 'od du gtan la phab kyang 'gal ba med /
NK104(phe)001:12900: thugs rje zer du gtan la phab kyang sems can gyi snang ngo'i ngos nas 'gal ba med do //
NK104(phe)001:12901: de yang ka nas dag pas gzhi /
NK104(phe)001:12902: gsal ba rang rdzogs pas lam /
NK104(phe)001:12903: ldog bya dang ldog byed med pas 'bras bu zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:12904: de yang ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gzhi
NK104(phe)001:12905: nas 'di ltar snang ba rang dag pas ka dag
NK104(phe)001:12906: ces bya'o // zhes bzhi pa rdzogs pa chen po ka dag rang gnas chen po'i gzhi las /
NK104(phe)001:12909: thugs rje gsum gyi gnas tshul bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:12910: da ni lnga pa rdzogs pa chen po ka dag
NK104(phe)001:12911: rang gnas pa'i gzhi la blo btags pa'i chos gang
NK104(phe)001:12912: gis kyang mi snyegs par bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12913: de ltar dngos po'i 'dug tshul la /
NK104(phe)001:12914: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:12917: thugs rje gsum du gnas pa'i dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul la /
NK104(phe)001:12918: shes bya de gang zag gi dus na gzhal bya'i yul du byas nas /
NK104(phe)001:12919: ngo bo ka dag pa'i cha nas phar rang gi sems dang chos nyid 'dres pa la bltas pas /
NK104(phe)001:12920: de la gang yang 'dzin cing grub pa med pa'i gnas kyis /
NK104(phe)001:12921: snying po'i don rang la rdzogs pas dge ba bcu dang /
NK104(phe)001:12922: dngos po 'dug tshul de bcos ma las grol bas mi dge ba bcu'ang med /
NK104(phe)001:12923: de la dbugs phyi nang du 'gyu ba med pas srog med pas skye shi med /
NK104(phe)001:12924: rnam par rtog pa rang kar 'dzin pa'i lus med
NK104(phe)001:12925: pas gcod pa'i 'du shes bral bas na stong pa
NK104(phe)001:12926: ngo bo nges gzung las 'das pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:12927: de nyid rang gang gi ngo bor kyang grub pa
NK104(phe)001:12928: med pas 'di dang 'di'i rtsis gdab las 'das so
NK104(phe)001:12929: // dmigs pa yul la 'dzin pa gang yang mi mdzad pas snang ba'i bdag por gnas pa /
NK104(phe)001:12930: cir yang shar la cir yang grol bas na /
NK104(phe)001:12931: rol pa sna tshogs pa rang shar rang grol la /
NK104(phe)001:12932: de ltar gnas pa'i gzhi de la /
NK104(phe)001:12933: tshig dang bcas pa'i lta ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:12934: tshig gis dmigs gtad dang bcas pa'i bsgom pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12935: tshig gis blang dor dang bcas pa'i spyod pas kyang
NK104(phe)001:12936: 'di dang phyogs 'gal bas gang la yang mi gnas
NK104(phe)001:12937: so // de dag rnams kyis chos nyid ka nas
NK104(phe)001:12938: dag pa de'i phyogs cha tsam yang mthong ba med
NK104(phe)001:12939: so // do // gzhi de rtsa ba'i sngags dang bsnyen bsgrub byas pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12940: ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pas goms pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12941: bsam gtan la mnyam par gzhag pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK104(phe)001:12942: ka dag pa'i chos nyid de'i gra la reg par mi 'gyur ro //
NK104(phe)001:12943: de nyid rgyu'i dus na yang sbyin pa gtang ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:12947: bsam gtan la mnyam par gzhag pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12948: shes rab sbyangs pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK104(phe)001:12949: gzhi ka nas dag pa 'di la phan pa dang gnod pa bral te /
NK104(phe)001:12950: dper na nam mkha' la mdung skor ba lta bu'o /
NK104(phe)001:12951: ka dag chen po la tshig med pa'i gnad kyis tshig gis rgyud dang /
NK104(phe)001:12953: man ngag gis kyang dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul /
NK104(phe)001:12954: 'di la dgos pa rdul phra rab kyi cha tsam yang med do //
NK104(phe)001:12955: de'i phyir na tshig gis sangs mi rgya ba'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:12956: ka dag bya byed dang 'bral bas spros bcas dang /
NK104(phe)001:12958: shin tu spros pa med pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12959: rab tu spros pa med pa'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:12963: phyi nang gsang ba'i sdom pa phog pas kyang /
NK104(phe)001:12964: ka nas dag pa'i gzhi 'di la phan pa dang gnod pa yang ma bskyal bas na /
NK104(phe)001:12965: gzhi nyid kyi don de gnyen po gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:12968: ma 'ongs pa'i dus gsum bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang /
NK104(phe)001:12969: 'di nyid sngar sus kyang mthong ba med pas na 'khor 'das gnyis su byung ba'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:12970: zhes lnga pa rdzogs pa chen po ka dag rang
NK104(phe)001:12971: gnas pa'i gzhi la blos btags pa'i chos gang gis
NK104(phe)001:12973: da ni drug pa rdzogs pa chen po ka dag
NK104(phe)001:12974: rang gnas pa'i gzhi gang gis kyang mi rtogs pa
NK104(phe)001:12975: de chos nyid mngon sum gyi don mthong ba tsam
NK104(phe)001:12976: gyis shes par bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:12978: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:12979: gang gis kyang mi rnyed pa de'i phyiir na dngos gzhi 'di /
NK104(phe)001:12980: spros pa rang rgyud pa'i tshig gis gtan la dbab par dka' ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:12981: de la brjod pas de'i thog tu phebs pa med pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:12982: de nyid blo'i yul du ma gyur pa'i phyir bsams pas de'i rjes mi chod de /
NK104(phe)001:12983: 'o na gtan mi rtogs sam zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12984: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag chos nyid mngon sum
NK104(phe)001:12985: gyis thabs bstan nas de la gang gis goms pa
NK104(phe)001:12987: de yang ji ltar rtogs zhe na /
NK104(phe)001:12988: dper na rdo rje gdan ma mthong kyang /
NK104(phe)001:12989: de'i lam ma nor bar zhugs nas phyin pas /
NK104(phe)001:12990: mtshan nyid bshad mi dgos par mtshan nyid gtan la phebs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK104(phe)001:12991: de lta bu'i mngon sum gyi thabs la goms pa
NK104(phe)001:12992: gang gis kyang byas pa'i skal ldan 'dis ni skyes
NK104(phe)001:12993: bu 'phangs rlabs che bas mda' 'phangs pa slar mi
NK104(phe)001:12995: skal ldan de yang khams gsum 'khor ba slar ldog
NK104(phe)001:12996: pa ma yin no zhes sangs rgya bar nges so
NK104(phe)001:12997: // zhes bsdus pa'i don tha ma la drug tu byas nas bstan no //
NK104(phe)001:12998: zhes kun tu bzang po la sogs pa mtshan gyi skabs su bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:12999: de dag gis le'u'i gzhung la bsdus pa'i don gsum du byas nas bstan no //
NK104(phe)001:13001: gzhi ni ma bcos shing mi 'gyur ba la gnas pa la bzhag la /
NK104(phe)001:13002: dngos po'i ni 'dra men nam gzugs brnyan lta bu ma yin pa la bya /
NK104(phe)001:13003: gnas lugs sku gsum gyi gnas chos nyid las lugs su byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13004: gtan la rdzogs pa chen po gzhi 'dod pa rang
NK104(phe)001:13005: shar ba'i ngos nas bsam gyis mi khyab pa cig
NK104(phe)001:13006: yod kyi lhun grub la sogs pa bdun du phab
NK104(phe)001:13007: pa'i klong brjod bya bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan
NK104(phe)001:13008: pa'o // de lta bu'i gzhung tshig dang yi ge
NK104(phe)001:13009: ris su bris pa le'u dang bcas pa bstan pa
NK104(phe)001:13010: zhes bya ba bstan zin zhes pa ste ni lhag
NK104(phe)001:13012: ma 'ongs pa sdud par byed pa nas /
NK104(phe)001:13013: lnga pa la sogs pa yang ston zhes pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13014: bzhi pa ni gsum las gzhan du gyur pa /
NK104(phe)001:13015: rdzogs so ni gnas skabs kyi gzhung dum bu lhag
NK104(phe)001:13016: ma ma lus par rdzogs zhes pa bstan du med
NK104(phe)001:13018: byol ba ni dge ba las byol nas 'bras bu
NK104(phe)001:13019: ngan song du song bas de'i duhkha nyams su myong
NK104(phe)001:13024: dam pa'i chos la yang dag tu ma mthong bas skye gnas ngan par 'khor la /
NK104(phe)001:13025: nges tshig dge ba las byol nas mi dge ba'i
NK104(phe)001:13026: ngang du rang bzhin gyis song bas na byol song
NK104(phe)001:13029: kha 'thor ba'i byol song gnyis so //
NK104(phe)001:13033: bud+d+ha dang dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rgyab kyis phyogs pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13034: dge ba las byol nas ngan song du song ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13035: bye brag tu las kyi lan so tha dad pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13040: de bzhin du de dag gcig dang /
NK104(phe)001:13053: mi tshe dang mnyam pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13054: lha'i tshe dang mnyam pa yang yod do //
NK104(phe)001:13056: smra bsam la dbang ma thob ste /
NK104(phe)001:13057: dper na lkugs pa la shes rig yod kyang lce
NK104(phe)001:13058: yis smra mi shes pas rab tu sdug pa lta
NK104(phe)001:13059: bu la spyod / snang ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:13060: rtag tu mun pa lta bur snang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:13061: de la byings na gnas pa'i byol song ni /
NK104(phe)001:13062: gling gling gi bar na gnas te /
NK104(phe)001:13063: de dag na nyi ma dang zla ba'i snang bas ma khyab ste /
NK104(phe)001:13064: rtag tu mtshan mo lta bur mun pa la gnas /
NK104(phe)001:13065: la la gzugs dpag tshad tsam la /
NK104(phe)001:13066: kha na so spu gri lta bu /
NK104(phe)001:13067: lus mgo mjug khas khengs pas ci phrad phrad za bar byed par yod do //
NK104(phe)001:13068: la la lus khab tsam la /
NK104(phe)001:13069: lus thams cad yan lag lcags kyu'i rnam pa dang 'dra bas khengs pa /
NK104(phe)001:13070: gang phrad phrad 'dzin par byed pa /
NK104(phe)001:13072: la la lus la mtshon cha sna tshogs pa'i spu yod pa /
NK104(phe)001:13073: skabs su spu de dag gis gzhan gyi lus la zug par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13074: la la lus kyi stod smad kyi bye brag la me 'brug cing /
NK104(phe)001:13075: stod smad gang yang rung ba chus 'brug cing /
NK104(phe)001:13076: skabs su spu de dag gis gzhan gyi lus la zug par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13077: la la lus kyi stod smad kyi bye brag la me 'brug cing /
NK104(phe)001:13078: stod smad gang yang rung ba chus 'brug cing /
NK104(phe)001:13079: tsha reg dang grang reg gi duhkha dus gcig la nyams su myong ba yod la /
NK104(phe)001:13081: lus phub lta bur rab tu zlum zhing leb pa la /
NK104(phe)001:13082: mtha' ma yan lag lcags kyu dang 'dra ba mang por 'khor ba /
NK104(phe)001:13083: gang phrad phrad 'dzin par byed cing mi gtong ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13084: yang la la lus bsre khab kyi rnam pa lta
NK104(phe)001:13085: bu la lus kyi rked pa rnams khas 'khor ba
NK104(phe)001:13086: la mche ba spu gri'i rnam pa lta bus gtams
NK104(phe)001:13087: pa / gzhan gang rnyed pa za bar byed cing
NK104(phe)001:13088: las kyi bye brag 'dod sems rab tu che ba
NK104(phe)001:13089: pa / las byung ba'o // yang la la lus dpag tshad lnga bcu yod pa la /
NK104(phe)001:13090: yan lag gcig las med pa'i 'gro bar 'dod kyang
NK104(phe)001:13091: yan lag gcig po des mi theg pa las kyi
NK104(phe)001:13092: bye brag yul 'brog la bdag tu gzung zhing rlom
NK104(phe)001:13093: pa che ba las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13094: yang la la lus gri gug gi rnam pa dang 'dra ba la /
NK104(phe)001:13095: mchu lcags mchu'i rnam pa dang 'dra bar gzhan la zug par byed pa /
NK104(phe)001:13096: las kyi bye brag grub pa'i mtha' la skur pa btab pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13097: yang la la lus 'khor lo'i rnam pa dang 'dra ba la /
NK104(phe)001:13098: rab tu 'khor ba'i sgra byung bas gzhan sgras skrag par byed pa //
NK104(phe)001:13099: las kyi bye brag rgyal po longs spyod dang ldan pa'i lus las /
NK104(phe)001:13100: dam chos gtso ma byas pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13101: yang la la lus rdza rnga'i rnam pa dang 'dra
NK104(phe)001:13102: ba la rab tu gzir ba'i sgra dang bud pa'i
NK104(phe)001:13103: sgra yod pa / las kyi bye brag tshul bzhin
NK104(phe)001:13104: ma yin pa'i bardzu rlabs po che las chos yid
NK104(phe)001:13105: la ma dran pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13106: la la lus gcig la mgo drug yod pa las
NK104(phe)001:13107: kyi bye brag ma byin par blang shing chos yid
NK104(phe)001:13108: la ma dran pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13109: la la lus gcig la mgo bcu dang nyer gcig
NK104(phe)001:13110: yod pa la sogs pa'i lus dpag tu med pa
NK104(phe)001:13111: rnams ni / las kyi bye brag 'dod sems khong
NK104(phe)001:13112: du bcug cing zhe la bzhag nas chos yid la
NK104(phe)001:13113: ma dran pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13114: la la lus gcig la mgo gnyis /
NK104(phe)001:13119: bcu la sogs pa yod pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:13120: las kyi bye brag yul mtha' khob las skye ba 'khor ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13121: la la lus mda' bo che lta bu dang /
NK104(phe)001:13122: mdung dang gtun shig lta bu yod pa rnams sngon
NK104(phe)001:13123: chad kyang byol song rang gi lus las 'khor ba'o
NK104(phe)001:13124: // de dag la sogs te gzugs kyi bye brag brjod kyi mi lang ba rnams ni /
NK104(phe)001:13125: las kyi bye brag dam pa'i chos la rgyal kyis phyogs pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13126: de dag gi spyod lam gyi khyad par ni /
NK104(phe)001:13127: la la ltos 'gro zhing yan lag med pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13128: la la nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13130: la la spyi tshugs su 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13131: la la zur gyis 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13132: la la mche ba rab tu che ba sa la btsugs nas 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13133: la la skad bton pa tsam la brten nas 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13134: la la dbugs 'gyus pa tsam la brten nas rang dbang med par 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13135: la la spu sa la rig pa tsam gyis 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13136: la la yan lag brkyang pa tsam gyis rang dbang med par 'gro ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13138: thang la reg pa tsam gyis rang dbang med par 'gro ba la sogs te dpag tu med do //
NK104(phe)001:13139: de dag kyang snga ma la 'gro ba gzhan gyi
NK104(phe)001:13140: tshul bzhin ma yin pa'i spyod pa las 'gro ba'i
NK104(phe)001:13141: bye brag de dag byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13143: gling bar gyi mun pa'i phyi'i rgya mtsho'i nang na chang ngar ba'i spang ma tsam mo //
NK104(phe)001:13145: gcig gi sha la gcig za ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13146: de'ang gcig gi rkang pa nas gcig gis za tsam na /
NK104(phe)001:13147: des gzhan gyi lus la za /
NK104(phe)001:13148: des kyang gzhan gcig la za ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13149: ya nga re re la bcu bcu za ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13150: gcig la gcig za ba'i duhkha mang ngo //
NK104(phe)001:13152: rgya mtsho'i nang na gnas la /
NK104(phe)001:13157: de dag ni skye ba bzhi kar skye ba len par byed pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13158: kha 'thor ba'i byol song 'di dag ni 'byung ba la dbang sgyur ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13159: lus la dbang sgyur ba gnyis so //
NK104(phe)001:13160: 'byung ba chu la dbang ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13164: lus su grub tshad gyi lto'i nang na byol song
NK104(phe)001:13165: gi srin phra mo nyi khri chig stong yod do
NK104(phe)001:13166: // 'di la rigs ni rkang mngas dang /
NK104(phe)001:13167: 'di dag las kyi bye brag 'gro ba la dga'
NK104(phe)001:13168: zhig chos yid la ma dran pa las byung ba'o
NK104(phe)001:13169: // rkang med kyi rigs stong phrag lnga yod de //
NK104(phe)001:13170: las kyi bye brag gnas gcig tu chos yid la ma dran pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13171: sder chags kyi rigs la stong phrag bcu gcig yod de /
NK104(phe)001:13172: 'di dag kyang bya ba ma yin pa las sna tshogs pa bya ba las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13173: mche ba can gyi rigs stong phrag bdun yod de /
NK104(phe)001:13174: 'di dag kyang snga ma la rab tu 'phro zhing chos yid la ma dran pa nas byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13175: ya gshog pa can gyi rigs khri phrag gcig yod de /
NK104(phe)001:13176: 'di dag kyang 'gro ba las kyi bye brag tha dad pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13177: rmigs pa can gyi rigs la stong phrag gsum yod do //
NK104(phe)001:13178: 'di dag ni las kyi bye brag 'du shes las kyi mtha' 'khor ba las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13179: dbang po'i yul du gyur ba dang /
NK104(phe)001:13180: ma gyur ba la sogs pa'i bye brag dpag tu med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13181: 'di ni dam pa'i chos la rgyab kyis bltas pa las byung ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13182: de dag kyang 'gro ba gzhan gyi dbang du byas pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13183: gcig la gcig dbang du byas pa la sogs pa
NK104(phe)001:13184: so so'i las kyi mtha' sna tshogs pa yod do
NK104(phe)001:13185: // 'di yang byol song gi 'gro ba las kyi mtha' 'khor ba ni /
NK104(phe)001:13186: la la byol song rang du 'khor la /
NK104(phe)001:13187: la la sems can dmyal bar 'khor ba yang yod /
NK104(phe)001:13188: la la yi dwags su 'khor ba la sogs pa'o /
NK104(phe)001:13191: shin tu phra ba la sogs pa dbang po'i spyod
NK104(phe)001:13192: yul du ma gyur ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK104(phe)001:13196: sems can gzhan gyi lus la gnas so //
NK104(phe)001:13200: snang ba ma dag pa'i duhkha bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13201: de dag shes pas de nyid du mi 'jug pas na /
NK104(phe)001:13202: 'di nyid shes pa tsam gyis de rnam par dag
NK104(phe)001:13203: par byed pa'i las ni 'di shes pas grol ba
NK104(phe)001:13204: chen po'i gnad la khams gsum ming med pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13205: de yang byol song gi skye gnas kyi mtshan nyid
NK104(phe)001:13206: ma mthong na de nyid du phyis 'jug par 'gyur
NK104(phe)001:13207: bas na / da lta 'di nyid du gtan la
NK104(phe)001:13208: phebs pas phyis byol song gi skye ba len mi
NK104(phe)001:13209: srid pas rab tu gal che'o //
NK104(phe)001:13210: des na shes pas grol ba'i shes grol chen po la phyi nas ldogs med pa'i gnad do //
NK104(phe)001:13214: ste zhes lhag ma can gyi tshig ste /
NK104(phe)001:13215: 'di ma yin pa gzhan yang ston zhes bya'o //
NK104(phe)001:13218: gsum las gzhan du gyur pa grangs kyi bye brag ste /
NK104(phe)001:13220: rin po che gsal ba'i phreng las /
NK104(phe)001:13221: klong bzhi pa'i don gsal bar byed pa /
NK104(phe)001:13222: 'di las zab pa 'dzam gling gzhan na med pas yid ches so //
NK104(phe)001:13228: ga6bakhi3dah&a&a&a da ni rin po che gsal ba'i phreng ba las /
NK104(phe)001:13229: klong lnga pa snying po lam dang 'bras bu rang grol bar bstan pa'i don bstan pa la /
NK104(phe)001:13231: dbang po yangs pa chos nyid kyi rdzogs pa chen
NK104(phe)001:13232: po snying po yongs su rdzogs pa'i klong bstan pa
NK104(phe)001:13233: dang / gnyis pa lnga ldan rdzogs pa chen po
NK104(phe)001:13234: ye shes lnga'i rol pa sna tshogs shar ba'i klong
NK104(phe)001:13235: dang / bstan pa dang / gsum pa 'khor ba
NK104(phe)001:13236: dong sprugs pa'i rdzogs pa chen po chos thams cad
NK104(phe)001:13237: mya ngan las 'das pa'i klong du thams cad ma
NK104(phe)001:13238: grol ba med par bstan pa'o //
NK104(phe)001:13239: de la yangs pa chos nyid kyi rdzogs pa chen
NK104(phe)001:13240: po snying po yongs su rdzogs pa'i klong bstan pa
NK104(phe)001:13241: la / nang don drug gis bstan pa'i dang po //
NK104(phe)001:13242: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byin brlabs rnam par snang ba rang bzhin gyi chos nyid bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:13243: de nas ston pa kun tu bzang pos /
NK104(phe)001:13244: zhes pa la sogs pa bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:13245: de nas ni klong bzhi'i don bstan pa'i de nas zhes bya la /
NK104(phe)001:13246: ston pa yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pa la dmigs pa /
NK104(phe)001:13247: kun tu mang po las khyad par du 'dus pa /
NK104(phe)001:13248: bzang pos ni rnam par rtog pa ngan pa las
NK104(phe)001:13249: mi gnas pa chos nyid ni byas shing bcos ma
NK104(phe)001:13250: las grol ba / mnyam pa ni thugs rnam par
NK104(phe)001:13251: dag pa'i ye shes su ro gcig tu gyur pa
NK104(phe)001:13252: las grol ba / / chen po ni rdzogs chen
NK104(phe)001:13253: dgos 'dod rang rdzogs pa'i don las 'das sa med
NK104(phe)001:13254: las grol ba / / pa'o // rgyan 'od dang kha dog gis mdzes pa /
NK104(phe)001:13255: rnam par rol pa zhes bya ba'i ni /
NK104(phe)001:13256: phyi yul la rol pas cir snang chos nyid du shes la /
NK104(phe)001:13257: nang sems la rol pas sems nyid gang nas kyang
NK104(phe)001:13258: ma byung ma skyes par shes pa de nyid 'du
NK104(phe)001:13259: 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa ngo bos stong la /
NK104(phe)001:13260: rang bzhin gyis de nyid las ma g.yos thugs rjes
NK104(phe)001:13261: gang du'ang 'byed pa med pa la dus thams cad
NK104(phe)001:13262: du 'jol nyog tu gnas par gyur te /
NK104(phe)001:13264: mi sems par sngon byung du ston pa nyid bzhugs pas /
NK104(phe)001:13265: de'i byin brlabs las gong du bstan pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang /
NK104(phe)001:13266: yon tan dang phrin las kyi mdzad pas /
NK104(phe)001:13267: 'jig pa rlung gis 'jig la brten pa'ang rlung la brten la /
NK104(phe)001:13268: gyi khams sna tshogs 'dus shing mtha' yas pa /
NK104(phe)001:13270: dper na til gyi gang bu chung yang 'bras bu rab tu rgyas pas nang du gsal /
NK104(phe)001:13272: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi nang gi mdzad pa rtsal dang rol par /
NK104(phe)001:13273: sus kyang byas pa med par rang shar bas /
NK104(phe)001:13274: bya byed dang 'bad rtsol las grol /
NK104(phe)001:13275: yul dngos por 'dzin pa med par rang snang bas snang ba chos nyid du grol /
NK104(phe)001:13276: gnyen po med par rang grol bas snang shes gnyis ka rang thog nas grol /
NK104(phe)001:13277: bslabs pa med par rang rig pa tshig dang yi ge la ma brten par grol /
NK104(phe)001:13278: ma bsgrubs par rang thob nas slar khams gsum du mi ldog par grol ba'o //
NK104(phe)001:13279: zhes dang po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byin brlabs snang ba rang bzhin gyi chos nyid bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:13280: da ni gnyis pa 'jig rten pa'i 'khor rnams kyis
NK104(phe)001:13281: sangs rgyas gyi byin brlabs la brten pas chos nyid
NK104(phe)001:13282: kyi bden pa mthong ba'i lugs bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:13283: lha dang mi la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK104(phe)001:13284: zhes pa la sogs pa bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:13285: lha dang ni lha'i dbang po rgya byin la sogs
NK104(phe)001:13286: pa'am 'dod pa na spyod pa'i lha'i bu skal pa
NK104(phe)001:13288: lha'i bu rab tu snang byed la sogs te gzugs
NK104(phe)001:13289: na spyod pa'i lha'i bu skal pa yod pa rnams
NK104(phe)001:13290: dang / lha'i bu drang srong slar mi ldog pa la sogs te /
NK104(phe)001:13291: gzugs med pa na spyod pa'i lha'i bu skal pa yod pa rnams dang /
NK104(phe)001:13292: mi ru dga' rab rdo rje la sogs te /
NK104(phe)001:13293: mi'i bu rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i skal pa yod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13294: la sogs pa ni thag bzangs rigs la sogs pa'i lha min gyi bu skal pa yod pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13302: mi 'am ci la sogs pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK104(phe)001:13303: chen po'i skal pa yod pa rnams kyis kyang chos
NK104(phe)001:13304: nyid stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la rang
NK104(phe)001:13305: shugs kyi spyod pa la gnas nas /
NK104(phe)001:13306: 'di dag rnams la ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK104(phe)001:13307: ngo bo cir yang ma yin snyams pa'i nyams te /
NK104(phe)001:13308: tha mal pa'i shes pa rnams ci mi snyam pa'i
NK104(phe)001:13309: klong chos nyid 'byed pa med pa nyid du rang
NK104(phe)001:13310: dag nas ma byas pa'i bsam gtan la gnas te
NK104(phe)001:13311: / de'i chos nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK104(phe)001:13312: sus kyang ma byas pa rnam par rtog pa'i dri
NK104(phe)001:13313: ma rnams rang sangs dri ma 'chags pa'i rten med
NK104(phe)001:13314: / gang nas kyang ma byung bar rang sad pas khams gsum 'khor ba'i sa med /
NK104(phe)001:13315: gang nas kyang ma brtsal bar rang rnyed nas slar mi ldog pa'i sa thob ste /
NK104(phe)001:13316: rnam par rtog pa glo bur ba'i dran pa'i rgyun rnams dus gcig la chad do //
NK104(phe)001:13317: de chad pas 'das ma 'ongs da ltar la 'jug
NK104(phe)001:13318: pa'i bsam pa thams cad kyang rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK104(phe)001:13319: par dag nas / de'i tshe chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i dgongs pa rnams /
NK104(phe)001:13320: 'khor de dag gis skad cig tsam la gcig car du shes pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13322: la las khad kyis la brten nas rims kyis shes
NK104(phe)001:13323: pa yid kyi rnam shes 'gyu ba du ma'i rkyen
NK104(phe)001:13324: yal / la las sems sbyangs pa la brten nas
NK104(phe)001:13325: mthar chags su shes pa dang khams gsum 'khor bar
NK104(phe)001:13327: la las ngo sprod pa la brten nas thod rgal
NK104(phe)001:13328: du shes pa dang 'jig rten mthun pa'i snang ba
NK104(phe)001:13330: la las dgongs pa la brten nas ye dag tu
NK104(phe)001:13331: shes pa dang thog ma ka nas dag pa'i gnad
NK104(phe)001:13332: kyis ma rig pa 'khrul pa'i 'khor ba rgyun chad
NK104(phe)001:13333: / la las dgongs pa de nyid rang gnas pa
NK104(phe)001:13334: la brten nas ye gnas su shes pa dang sgo
NK104(phe)001:13335: lnga yul gyi shes pa dus cig la stong /
NK104(phe)001:13336: la las 'khor 'das dus cig la rtog pa la
NK104(phe)001:13337: brten nas ye rdzogs su shes pa dang mtha' rnams
NK104(phe)001:13338: las rang grol / la las rtsol sgrub med pa'i
NK104(phe)001:13339: chos nyid la brten nas ye byung du shes pa
NK104(phe)001:13340: dang 'phral 'byung gi nyon mongs rtsa ba nas stong
NK104(phe)001:13341: las rang grol / / la las phyi yul gyi
NK104(phe)001:13342: snang ba la brten nas ye bkod chen por rang
NK104(phe)001:13343: grol bar shes nas gnyen po dang re ltos gang
NK104(phe)001:13345: de ltar chos nyid kyi ngo bo mthong bas rang la rang ngo mtshar skyes nas /
NK104(phe)001:13346: de'i dus gzhi shes pa'i khyad par las rang la
NK104(phe)001:13347: rang yid ches skyes nas chos nyid kyi don mngon
NK104(phe)001:13348: sum du khong du chud do //
NK104(phe)001:13349: de ltar yid ches pas khams gsum du mi ldog
NK104(phe)001:13350: pa'i rang la rang stobs skyes nas da ni khams
NK104(phe)001:13351: gsum stongs pa a la la /
NK104(phe)001:13352: mi ldog chen po a la la /
NK104(phe)001:13353: byas med grol ba a la la /
NK104(phe)001:13355: 'khor de dag thams cad kyis ston pa kun tu
NK104(phe)001:13356: bzang po la mgrin cig tu gong ma'i tshig brjod
NK104(phe)001:13357: cing / lus thal mo snying khar sbyar nas /
NK104(phe)001:13358: yang tshig tu 'di skad ces zhus so //
NK104(phe)001:13360: 'khor bdag cag ni slar khams gsum du mi skye
NK104(phe)001:13361: ba'i chos la sus kyang ma bsgrubs pas rang bzhin
NK104(phe)001:13362: gyis mi ldog par shes pas bzod pa thob nas
NK104(phe)001:13363: / dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dang rang
NK104(phe)001:13364: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi
NK104(phe)001:13365: chos nyid zab mo dang skal pa mnyam par gyur
NK104(phe)001:13366: pa mchog tu ston pa'i byin brlabs la dga'/
NK104(phe)001:13367: rang gi sems kyi rtogs tshad mgu /
NK104(phe)001:13368: khams gsum du mi ldog pas yid rangs so zhes gsol nas /
NK104(phe)001:13369: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rnam par dag pa'i
NK104(phe)001:13370: chos nyid kyi dgongs pa dang dbyer mi phyed par
NK104(phe)001:13371: gyur to // zhes gnyis pa 'jig rten pa'i 'khor
NK104(phe)001:13372: gyis sangs rgyas kyi byin brlabs la brten nas chos
NK104(phe)001:13373: nyid kyi bden pa mthong ba'i lugs bstan nas /
NK104(phe)001:13374: da ni gsum pa sdud pa po rang gi mtshan
NK104(phe)001:13375: nyid dang bcas pas ston pa zhu ba lam du
NK104(phe)001:13376: 'bras bu'i dri ba mdor bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:13377: de nas 'khor de dag rnams kyi /
NK104(phe)001:13378: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:13379: de nas 'khor de dag rnams kyi ni 'jig rten pa'i 'khor gyi nang nas /
NK104(phe)001:13380: sngar sems bskyed pa'i stobs dang de'i sa bon ston
NK104(phe)001:13381: pa'i thugs kyi dgongs pa la brten pas lus ngag
NK104(phe)001:13382: yid kyi sdig pa ma lus pa byang nas /
NK104(phe)001:13383: lus ngag yid kyi dge ba ma lus pa rnams chub pas /
NK104(phe)001:13384: rtag tu rang gi don la sems pas chos nyid mngon sum du rtogs /
NK104(phe)001:13385: de nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du gzhan sems can
NK104(phe)001:13386: la brtse bas gzhan la sems pas dus thams cad
NK104(phe)001:13387: du snying rje chen po'i ngang las g.yos pa med
NK104(phe)001:13388: do // de yang rgyu gang las byung na /
NK104(phe)001:13389: thog ma stobs kyis rnam par rol pa 'khor ba
NK104(phe)001:13390: 'jigs pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams su yang dag
NK104(phe)001:13391: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'khor dam pa'i rnam par
NK104(phe)001:13393: rang gi 'khor rnams la chos ston pa zhig la /
NK104(phe)001:13394: byang chub sems dpa' 'di bcom ldan 'das glang po
NK104(phe)001:13395: che'i khri steng na mngon par bzhugs pa'i dus na
NK104(phe)001:13396: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de nyid la glang po
NK104(phe)001:13397: che yid du 'ong ba mdzes shing lta na sdug
NK104(phe)001:13398: pa / 'gro ba 'dod pa che ba rnams kyi yid 'phrog pa gcig la /
NK104(phe)001:13399: rin po che'i rgyan du mas rab tu brgyan /
NK104(phe)001:13400: mgul la sogs pa rnams dung gser gyi dril bu g.yer ka'i dra bas bres nas /
NK104(phe)001:13401: de'i khyim bdag gi bu dpal dang ldan pa zhes bya bar gyur te /
NK104(phe)001:13402: glang po che de phul nas sems bskyed zhus pas /
NK104(phe)001:13403: bcom ldan 'das des sems bskyed pas /
NK104(phe)001:13404: glang po che'i phru gu de las 'od zer dpag tu med pa rang bzhin gyis byung bas /
NK104(phe)001:13405: 'khor de dag gis bud+d+ha'i zhing khams gzhan dag kyang mthong bar gyur te /
NK104(phe)001:13406: 'khor rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das de la dris pa /
NK104(phe)001:13407: kye bcos ldan 'das 'di lta bu ci'i rgyu las 'byung ba lags zhes zhus pa dang /
NK104(phe)001:13408: bcom ldan 'das 'khor lo dam pa rnam par rol pas bka' stsal ba /
NK104(phe)001:13409: 'khor rnams nyon cig /'od zer gyi tshogs de dag
NK104(phe)001:13410: rab tu 'phros pas sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams gzhan
NK104(phe)001:13411: mngon par snang bar gyur pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:13412: khyim bdag gi bu 'dis nga la glang po che'i
NK104(phe)001:13413: phru gu 'di phul nas sems bskyed byas pa las
NK104(phe)001:13415: 'di ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus na yang dag par
NK104(phe)001:13416: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK104(phe)001:13417: zhes bya ba'i 'khor du byang chub sems dpa' chen
NK104(phe)001:13418: po glang po che'i 'od zer rab tu snang byed
NK104(phe)001:13419: ces bya ba'i byang chub sems dpar gyur nas sems
NK104(phe)001:13420: can rnams kyi don byed par 'gyur ro zhes lung
NK104(phe)001:13421: bstan no // de ltar sems bskyed pa sngon du
NK104(phe)001:13422: rdzogs pa las byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' glang
NK104(phe)001:13423: po'i 'od zer snang byed ces bya ba ston pa
NK104(phe)001:13424: kun tu bzang po'i 'khor de dag gi nang nas
NK104(phe)001:13425: bstan no // langs te / bla gos legs par
NK104(phe)001:13426: gyon nas ston pa la 'di ska da ces gsol
NK104(phe)001:13427: bstan no // langs te / te // zhu ba gsum zhus pa ni gzhung ni gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:13428: zhes gsum pa sdud pa rang gi ming gi gyon
NK104(phe)001:13429: mtshan nyid dang bcas pas ston pa la zhu ba
NK104(phe)001:13430: lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i dri ba mdor bstan
NK104(phe)001:13431: nas / de nyid bzhi pa ston pas lan du
NK104(phe)001:13432: chos nyid bcos ma las grol ba'i klong las snying
NK104(phe)001:13433: po nges pa'i don la 'jug ngo shes par bya
NK104(phe)001:13434: ba'i phyir chos kun yang dag gi snying po rtsol
NK104(phe)001:13435: ba las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK104(phe)001:13436: de las ston pa kun tu bzang po //
NK104(phe)001:13437: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK104(phe)001:13438: tshig gsung gzhung na gsal lo //
NK104(phe)001:13439: sdud pa po la kye zhes rang don du rtogs par gyis shig ces gdams la /
NK104(phe)001:13440: kye zhes de ltar rang don rtogs nas gzhan don
